-dick-17576%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESmithsonian.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20end%20in%20sight%20for%20sailors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20incidents%20between%20humans%20and%20the%20orca%20pod%20in%20the%20Strait%20of%20Gibraltar%20have%20occurred%20over%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theca.org.uk%2Forcas%2Finteraction-deterrent-library%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECruising%20Association%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20no%20end%20in%20immediate%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20recently%2C%20orcas%20targeted%20a%20Polish%20yacht%20for%2045%20minutes%20and%20caused%20major%20damage%20to%20the%20vessel.%20Crew%20members%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Forca-attacks-polish-yacht-sinking-it-morocco-killer-whales-2023-11%3F_gl%3D1*4dgsoj*_ga*NTExMzU3MzY2LjE2OTM2MTI2OTk.*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTcwMDYxOTYxNi44NjcuMS4xNzAwNjIwMDY0LjM3LjAuMA..%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BGrazie%20Mamma%20II%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewere%20safe%2C%20but%20the%20boat%20eventually%20sank%20after%20arriving%20at%20a%20Moroccan%20port.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20clear%20exactly%20why%20the%20orcas%20are%20adamant%20about%20targeting%20boats%2C%20but%20researchers%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it's%20likely%20that%20the%20whales%20are%20using%20the%20boats%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-killer-whales-orcas-attack-sink-boats-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocialize%20and%20play%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20the%20whales%20don't%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-atlantic-orca-story-reactions-killer-whales-sadistic-jerks-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edark%20intentions%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20ramming%20into%20boats%2C%20their%20presence%20is%20frustrating%20for%20sailor