t%20has%20approved%20a%20hostage%20deal%20%E2%80%94%20a%20major%20diplomatic%20breakthrough%20amid%20the%20war.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20outline%20includes%20the%20release%20of%2050%20hostages%20who%20are%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20deal%20comes%20as%20Israeli%20forces%20continue%20their%20extensive%20ground%20operations%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20cabinet%20approved%20a%20hostage%20release%20deal%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%20local%20time%2C%20a%20major%20diplomatic%20breakthrough%20that%20comes%20more%20than%20six%20weeks%20into%20the%20devastating%20war%20between%20the%20two%20sides.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Israel's%20government%20said%20it%20approved%20the%20outline%20of%20the%20first%20stage%20of%20an%20agreement%20that%20will%20see%20the%20release%20of%2050%20hostages%20who%20were%20abducted%20by%20Hamas%20during%20its%20October%207%20terror%20attacks%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20four-day%20ceasefire.%20The%20government%20added%20that%20the%20pause%20in%20fighting%20would%20extend%20for%20one%20day%20for%20every%2010%20hostages%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20150%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20held%20by%20Israel%20would%20be%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Government%20of%20Israel%2C%20the%20IDF%2C%20and%20the%20security%20services%20will%20continue%20the%20war%20in%20order%20to%20return%20home%20all%20of%20the%20hostages%2C%20complete%20the%20elimination%20of%20Hamas%2C%20and%20ensure%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20new%20threat%20to%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20from%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Israeli%20government%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20tentative%20agreement%2C%20it%20remains%20unclear%20exactly%20when%20the%20hostage%20and%20prisoner%20exchange%20will%20be%20completed.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Flive-blog%2Fisrael-hamas-war-live-updates-rcna126110%23rcrd26266%5C%22%3ENBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20the%20families%20of%20hostages%20will%20have%2024%20hours%20to%20appeal%20to%20Israel's%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20object%20to%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20groundbreaking%20development%20follows%20weeks%20of%20intense%20negotiations%20and%20high-level%20engagement%20involving%20Israel%2C%20the%20US%2C%20Qatar%2C%20and%20Egypt%2C%20a%20senior%20Biden%20administration%20official%20told%20reporters%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20deal%20involves%20only%20the%2050%20women%20and%20children.%20The%20pause%20in%20fighting%20could%20be%20extended%20if%20Hamas%20releases%20more%20hostages%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamas%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20holding%20around%20240%20hostages%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Israelis%2C%20Americans%2C%20and%20other%20foreign%20nationals%20%E2%80%94%20who%20were%20captured%20during%20the%20militant%20group's%20brutal%20rampage%2C%20which%20left%20over%201%2C200%20people%20dead.%20The%20Israeli%20government%20has%20been%20under%20widespread%20domestic%20pressure%20to%20secure%20their%20release%2C%20while%20protests%20and%20demonstrations%20have%20sprouted%20in%20major%20cities%20around%20the%20world%20in%20a%20show%20of%20solidarity%20with%20the%20hostages%20and%20their%20families.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20meets%20with%20soldiers%20as%20he%20visits%20an%20Israeli%20army%20base%20in%20Tze'elim%2C%20Israel%20November%207%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655d2b689c7d23cb3b9e7f77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22987%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20meets%20with%20soldiers%20as%20he%20visits%20an%20Israeli%20army%20base%20in%20Tze'elim%2C%20Israel%20November%207%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Government%20Press%20Office%2FHaim%20Zach%2FHandout%20via%20REUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20provided%20Israel%20with%20both%20diplomatic%20support%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpentagon-mq-9-reaper-drones-gaza-searching-hamas-hostages-2023-11%5C%22%3Eaerial%20surveillance%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20with%20its%20hostage%20recovery%20efforts.%20White%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%20Spokesperson%20John%20Kirby%20told%20reporters%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20Biden%20administration%20was%20working%20%26quot%3Bhour%20by%20hour%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdoing%20everything%20we%20can%26quot%3B%20to%20secure%20their%20release.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20office%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIsraeliPM%2Fstatus%2F1726964284260012443%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20between%206%20p.m.%20and%208%20p.m.%20local%20time%20he%20will%20convene%20the%20country's%20war%20cabinet%2C%20security%20cabinet%2C%20and%20government%2C%20in%20three%20separate%20meetings.%20The%20office%20said%20the%20announcement%20comes%20%26quot%3Bin%20light%20of%20developments%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20release%20of%20our%20hostages%2C%26quot%3B%20indicating%20that%20a%20deal%20may%20be%20in%20reach.%20Four%20hostages%20have%20already%20been%20released%20from%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmi%20Palmor%2C%20who%20previously%20served%20as%20the%20director%20general%20of%20Israel's%20Ministry%20of%20Justice%20and%20has%20experience%20on%20a%20hostage%20negotiation%20team%2C%20said%20this%20could%20end%20up%20being%20the%20only%20deal%20that%20the%20country%20manages%20to%20reach%20with%20Hamas%2C%20and%20its%20also%20uncertain%20if%20the%20militant%20group%20will%20actually%20honor%20its%20agreements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20do%20its%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20decisions%20are%20extremely%20difficult%20and%20it's%20a%20risk%20management%20because%2C%20I%20think%20that%20even%20without%20saying%20this%2C%20everyone%20understands%20that%20we%20are%20playing%20with%20the%20devil.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Israeli%20soldier%20rides%20in%20a%20tank%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20ground%20operation%20against%20Hamas%20in%20this%20handout%20image%20released%20November%2020%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655d2b1b4ca513d8242d5753%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Israeli%20soldier%20rides%20in%20a%20tank%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20ground%20operation%20against%20Hamas%20in%20this%20handout%20image%20released%20November%2020%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EIsrael%20Defense%20Forces%2FHandout%20via%20REUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20a%20pause%20in%20the%20ongoing%20fighting%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Israeli%20officials%20vow%20will%20continue%20until%20Hamas%20is%20ultimately%20destroyed%20%E2%80%94%20will%20play%20out%20remains%20unclear.%20The%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20is%20several%20weeks%20into%20its%20ground%20offensive%20and%20controls%20large%20swaths%20of%20territory%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20while%20its%20warplanes%20continue%20to%20bombard%20the%20coastal%20enclave%2C%20where%20over%2012%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20since%20the%20war%20began%20in%20early%20October.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIDF%20Chief%20of%20the%20General%20Staff%20Lt.%20Gen.%20Herzi%20Halevi%20told%20reserve%20soldiers%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20ground%20operations%20in%20Gaza%20are%20creating%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20conditions%26quot%3B%20for%20bringing%20back%20hostages.%20%26quot%3BIt%20hurts%20Hamas%2C%20it%20creates%20pressure%2C%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20this%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Israel%20and%20the%20US%20have%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fas-eu-weighs-ceasefire-call-us-rejects-any-such-push-says-it-only-benefits-hamas%2F%5C%22%3Erejected%3C%2Fa%3E%20growing%20calls%20from%20the%20global%20community%20for%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20with%20the%20White%20House%20arguing%20that%20it%20benefits%20Hamas%20and%20gives%20the%20militant%20group%20time%20to%20regroup.%20The%20Biden%20administration%20has%2C%20however%2C%20managed%20to%20get%20the%20Israelis%20to%20agree%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F11%2F09%2Fisrael-humanitarian-pauses-gaza-00126355%5C%22%3Eshort%20pauses%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20to%20allow%20for%20civilians%20to%20evacuate%20northern%20Gaza%20and%20facilitate%20the%20movement%20of%20humanitarian%20aid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fighting%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20not%20been%20limited%20to%20Gaza%2C%20and%20has%20drawn%20in%20other%20Iran-backed%20militants%20like%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%20and%20the%20Houthis%20in%20Yemen.%20US%20forces%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Syria%20have%20also%20been%20attacked%20dozens%20of%20times%20over%20the%20past%20month%20by%20groups%20that%20are%20supported%20by%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20is%20developing.%20Please%20check%20back%20for%20updates.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-hostage-deal-major-diplomatic-breakthrough-gaza-war-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700619850000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655cf4384ca513d8242cfe92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-hostage-deal-major-diplomatic-breakthrough-gaza-war-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20statement%2C%20Israel's%20government%20said%20it%20approved%20the%20outline%20of%20the%20first%20stage%20of%20an%20agreement%20that%20will%20see%20the%20release%20of%2050%20hostages.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jepstein%40insider.com%20(Jake%20Epstein%2CKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-hostage-deal-major-diplomatic-breakthrough-gaza-war-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSlightly%20Better%20Pitch%20Would...%26quot%3B%3A%20Harbhajan's%20Firm%20Take%20On%20World%20Cup%20Final%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20'pitch%20talk'%20has%20been%20at%20the%20center%20of%20many%20debates%20since%20the%20semi-finals%20of%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023.%20First%2C%20it%20was%20the%20match%20between%20India%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20and%20then%20the%20final.%20After%20India%20went%20on%20to%20lose%20the%20summit%20clash%20to%20Australia%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20questions%20arose%20whether%20the%20curators%20could've%20prepared%20a%20better%20wicket%20for%20the%20final.%20When%20Harbhajan%20Singh%20was%20asked%20about%20his%20views%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20he%20also%20believed%20that%20the%20Indian%20team%20would've%20performed%20better%20if%20the%20pitch%20prepared%20was%20slightly%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20was%20the%20kind%20of%20pitch%20which%20was%20on%20the%20slower%20side.%20It%20was%20drier%20than%20the%20usual%20pitch.%20You%20know%2C%20I%20would%20have%20liked%20to%20see%20a%20pitch%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20scores%20like%20300%20plus%20been%20scored.%20That%20sort%20of%20pitch%20would%20have%20India%20more%20than%20this%20kind%20of%20pitch%20where%2C%20you%20know%2C%20you%20bring%20your%20opposition%20in%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Harbhajan%20said%20in%20a%20chat%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fvideo%2Fworld-cup-2023-final-4-boundaries-in-40-overs-is-where-the-game-changed-for-india-says-harbhajan-singh-2465477-2023-11-20%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%20where%20your%20batters%20were%20in%20such%20great%20form.%20They%20looked%20really%20good%20throughout%20the%20tournament%2C%20and%20they%20were%20fantastic%20and%20very%2C%20very%20proud%20of%20them.%20The%20way%20they%20play%20their%20cricket.%20I%20think%2C%20a%20slightly%20better%20pitch%20would%20help%20them%20to%20perform%20better%20than%20what%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20Harbhajan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20fact%20that%20Australia%20won%20the%20final%2C%20Bhajji%20feels%20India%20had%20the%20better%20team.%20If%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20wicket%20was%20similar%20to%20what%20has%20traditionally%20been%20the%20case%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20the%20result%20could've%20been%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20India%20was%20the%20superior%20side.%20You%20ask%20anyone.%20Yesterday%20before%20the%20game%2C%20I%20spoke%20to%20a%20couple%20of%20my%20Aussie%20friends%20who%20I%20played%20with%20in%20my%20era.%20And%20all%20of%20them%2C%20they%20said%2C%20India%20is%20just%20top%20side%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20India%20all%20the%20way%2C%20But%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20Australian%20team%20they%20came%20out%20with%20the%20plan%2C%20they%20executed%20well%2C%20and%20they%20played%20fantastic%20cricket.%20And%2C%20of%20course%2C%20if%20the%20wicket%20was%20on%20slightly%20on%20a%20better%20side%2C%20one%20with%20the%20ball%20coming%20nicely%20onto%20the%20bat%2C%20Uh%2C%20you%20know%2C%20I%20think%2C%20we%20would%20have%20enjoyed%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700619780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F9mgupkm_harbhajan-singh-youtube_625x300_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fslightly-better-pitch-would-harbhajan-singhs-honest-take-on-indias-world-cup-final-loss-4591682%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iconic%20Indian%20spinner%20Harbhajan%20Singh%20has%20weighed%20in%20on%20the%20'pitch%20debate'%20after%20India's%20defeat%20against%20Australia%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20final.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fslightly-better-pitch-would-harbhajan-singhs-honest-take-on-indias-world-cup-final-loss-4591682%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fslightly-better-pitch-would-harbhajan-singhs-honest-take-on-indias-world-cup-final-loss-4591682%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fslightly-better-pitch-would-harbhajan-singhs-honest-take-on-indias-world-cup-final-loss-4591682%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ICC%20Bans%20Transgender%20Players%20From%20International%20Women's%20Cricket%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20policy%20decision%2C%20The%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20on%20Tuesday%20banned%C2%A0transgender%20cricketers%20from%20participating%20in%20women's%20cricket%20at%20the%20highest%20level.%20Transgender%20players%20who%20have%20been%20through%20any%20form%20of%20male%20puberty%20will%20be%20prohibited%20from%20competing%20in%20international%20women's%20games%20regardless%20of%20whether%20or%20not%20they%20have%20undergone%20surgery%20or%20gender%20reassignment%20treatment%2C%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fsport%2F2023%2Fnov%2F21%2Ftransgender-players-banned-from-international-womens-cricket-by-icc%5C%22%3E%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20said%20it%20was%20taking%20the%20decision%20to%20protect%20the%20integrity%20of%20international%20women's%20game%20and%20the%20safety%20of%20players.%C2%A0The%20board%20finalised%20the%20new%20policy%20after%20a%20nine-month%20consultation%20process%20with%20cricket's%20stakeholders%2C%20with%20the%20final%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EICC%20chief%20executive%20Geoff%20Allardice%20explained%20the%20decision%20saying%2C%20''The%20changes%20to%20the%20gender%20eligibility%20regulations%20resulted%20from%20an%20extensive%20consultation%20process%20and%20is%20founded%20in%20science%20and%20aligned%20with%20the%20core%20principles%20developed%20during%20the%20review.%20Inclusivity%20is%20incredibly%20important%20to%20us%20as%20a%20sport%2C%20but%20our%20priority%20was%20to%20protect%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20international%20women's%20game%20and%20the%20safety%20of%20players.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20was%20the%20trigger%20for%20ICC%20to%20bring%20about%20this%20change%2C%20a%20source%20said%20it%20was%20due%20to%20''cricket's%20inclusion%20in%20the%202028%20Olympics.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20cricket%20will%20be%20an%20Olympic%20sport%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20governed%20by%20the%20Olympic%20guidelines.%20This%20gender%20issue%20is%20a%20huge%20one%20at%20global%20level.%20The%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20(IOC)%20has%20changed%20regulations%20and%20advised%20sports%20to%20implement%20regulations%20that%20are%20suitable%20for%20their%20sport%2C%20which%20is%20what%20we%20have%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20ICC%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20comes%20two%20months%20after%20Canada's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmeet-canadas-danielle-mcgahey-who-is-set-to-become-first-transgender-to-play-international-cricket-4345645%5C%22%3EDanielle%20McGahey%20became%20the%20first%20transgender%20cricketer%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20take%20part%20in%20an%20official%20international%20match%20when%20she%20featured%20in%20a%20Women's%20T20%20fixture%20against%20Brazil.%20However%2C%20she%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20participate%20in%20women's%20international%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20McGahey%20moved%20to%20Canada%20from%20Australia%20in%20February%202020%20and%20began%20her%20social%20transition%20from%20a%20man%20to%20a%20woman%20in%20November%202020.%20She%20started%20her%20medical%20transition%20in%20May%202021.%20Cricket%20Canada%20said%20McGahey%20was%20selected%20for%20the%20team%20as%20she%20fulfilled%20all%20ICC's%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20rules%C2%A0relate%20to%20gender%20eligibility%20for%20international%20women's%20cricket%20only.%20''The%20gender%20eligibility%20at%20the%20domestic%20level%20is%20a%20matter%20for%20each%20individual%20Member%20board%2C%20which%20may%20be%20impacted%20by%20local%20legislation%2C''%20the%20ICC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransgender%20athletes%20have%20been%20banned%20from%20taking%20part%20in%20elite%20women's%20competitions%20in%20other%20sports%20such%20as%20swimming%2C%20cycling%2C%20athletics%2C%20rugby%20league%2C%20and%20rugby%20union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700619660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F6saf4sto_danielle-mcgahey_625x300_31_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ficc-bans-transgender-players-from-international-womens-cricket-4594863%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ICC%20said%20it%20was%20taking%20the%20decision%20to%20protect%20the%20integrity%20of%20international%20women's%20game%20and%20the%20safety%20of%20players.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ficc-bans-transgender-players-from-international-womens-cricket-4594863%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ficc-bans-transgender-players-from-international-womens-cricket-4594863%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ficc-bans-transgender-players-from-international-womens-cricket-4594863%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGave%20Clear%20Message%20That...%26quot%3B%3A%20Pak%20Great%20On%20PM%20Modi's%20Team%20India%20Gesture%22%2C%22content%22%3A%