20would%20include%20a%20complete%20ceasefire%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20a%20pause%20in%20Israeli%20air%20operations%20over%20southern%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20cabinet's%20approval%20was%20one%20of%20the%20last%20stumbling%20blocks%20to%20the%20agreement%20coming%20into%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQatar%20had%20helped%20to%20broker%20the%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMisgivings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20vote%2C%20Netanyahu%20had%20faced%20a%20revolt%20from%20within%20his%20right-wing%20coalition%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20believe%20the%20agreement%20would%20give%20too%20much%20to%20Hamas%20operatives%20responsible%20for%20the%20worst%20attack%20in%20Israel's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardline%20Minister%20for%20National%20Security%20Itamar%20Ben-Gvir%20indicated%20he%20would%20vote%20against%20the%20agreement%2C%20saying%20it%20should%20include%20the%20release%20of%20Israeli%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20raids%20on%20October%207%20killed%20an%20estimated%201%2C200%20people%20and%20seized%20240%20hostages%2C%20civilians%20and%20military%2C%20who%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bloody%20attacks%20sparked%20Operation%20%26quot%3BSwords%20of%20Iron%26quot%3B%20--%20Israel's%20punishing%20air%20and%20ground%20on%20Hamas-run%20Gaza%2C%20which%20Palestinian%20authorities%20say%20has%20killed%2014%2C100%20people%2C%20mostly%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20dozens%20of%20families%20in%20Israel%20and%20beyond%20desperate%20to%20have%20their%20loved%20ones%20returned%20home%2C%20and%20the%20Israeli%20public%20gripped%20by%20the%20hostages'%20fate%2C%20the%20government%20set%20aside%20any%20misgivings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20powerful%20Defence%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20said%20before%20the%20crunch%20meeting%20that%20he%20had%20won%20assurances%20that%20the%20deal%20would%20not%20spell%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war%20to%20destroy%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImmediately%20after%20we%20have%20exhausted%20this%20phase%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20security%20operations%20would%20%26quot%3Bcontinue%20in%20full%20force.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Netanyahu's%20office%20underscored%20that%20the%20truce%20did%20not%20spell%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Israeli%20government%2C%20the%20Israeli%20army%20and%20the%20security%20forces%20will%20continue%20the%20war%20to%20bring%20back%20all%20those%20kidnapped%2C%20eliminate%20Hamas%20and%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20longer%20any%20threat%20to%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20from%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Unbearable%20situation'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Rafah%20resident%20Hamza%20Abdel%20Razeq%20welcomed%20any%20ceasefire%20would%20bring%20some%20respite%20for%20Gazans%20who%20have%20endured%20Israel's%20bombing%20and%20expanding%20ground%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20are%20really%20suffering%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20reach%20a%20five-day%20truce%20deal%20now%2C%20I%20believe%20it%20will%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20longer%20truces%20or%20even%20a%20total%20ceasefire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20resident%2C%20Mahmud%20Abu%20Najm%2C%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe...%20pray%20to%20God%20for%20its%20success%20because%20the%20people%20are%20enduring%20an%20unbearable%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELarge%20parts%20of%20Gaza%20have%20been%20flattened%20by%20thousands%20of%20air%20strikes%2C%20and%20the%20territory%20is%20under%20siege%2C%20with%20minimal%20food%2C%20water%20and%20fuel%20allowed%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Hamas%20and%20Islamic%20Jihad%20sources%2C%20the%20proposed%20deal%20would%20also%20allow%20for%20up%20to%20300%20trucks%20of%20food%20and%20medical%20aid%20to%20enter%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsr