20India%20were%20touted%20as%20the%20favourites%20to%20go%20the%20distance%20in%20the%20tournament%2C%20end%20their%2012-year%20wait%20of%20winning%20an%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20title.%20But%2C%20it%20was%20the%20Australian%20team%20that%20emerged%20triumphant.%20Speaking%20of%20the%20result%2C%20former%20Indian%20cricketer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20the%20best%20team%20actually%20went%20on%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20statements%20some%20other%20experts%20have%20been%20making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20believe%20that%20the%20Indian%20team%20was%20the%20best%20side%20in%20the%20tournament%20but%20a%20solitary%20defeat%20in%20the%20final%20prevented%20them%20from%20winning%20the%20title.%20Gambhir%2C%20however%2C%20doesn't%20think%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20might%20not%20like%20it.%20I%20heard%20some%20of%20the%20experts%20saying%20that%20the%20best%20team%20has%20not%20gone%20on%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup.%20That's%20absolutely%20not%20true.%20That's%20one%20of%20the%20bizarre%20statements%20that%20I%20have%20heard.%20It's%20actually%20the%20best%20team%20that%20has%20won%20the%20World%20Cup.%20Let's%20be%20honest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20chat%20on%20Sportskeeda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20won%2010%20matches%20and%20were%20in%20very%20good%20form%2C%20so%20they%20were%20favorites.%20But%20Australia%20had%20also%20won%20eight%20games%20in%20a%20row%20after%20losing%20the%20first%20two.%20Only%20the%20best%20team%20wins%20the%20World%20Cup.%20You%20cannot%20define%20it%20that%20way%20-%20that%20India%20won%2010%20matches%20but%20played%20one%20poor%20game.%20The%20reality%20is%20the%20semi-final%20and%20the%20final%20were%20the%20knockout%20matches.%20It%20did%20not%20matter%20whether%20you%20finished%20first%20or%20fourth%20%5Bin%20the%20league%20stage%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%2C%20in%20comparison%20to%20India%2C%20won%207%20of%20their%209%20matches%20in%20the%20league%20stage%20of%20the%20World%20Cup.%20They%20defeated%20South%20Africa%20comprehensively%20in%20the%20semi-final%20to%20book%20the%20final%20berth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20easy%20to%20win%20six%20out%20of%20eight%20league%20matches.%20Winning%20two%20out%20of%20two%20when%20you%20know%20any%20mistake%20can%20cost%20you%20is%20difficult.%20Let's%20accept%20that%20the%20best%20team%20has%20gone%20on%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup.%20India%20did%20not%20play%20well%2C%20let's%20not%20run%20away%20from%20reality%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700619300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Frvj5ggpo_gambhir_625x300_09_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fbest-team-won-the-world-cup-gautam-gambhir-slams-bizarre-statement-from-expert-4591445%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir%20doesn't%20think%20India%20had%20the%20'best%20team'%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fbest-team-won-the-world-cup-gautam-gambhir-slams-bizarre-statement-from-expert-4591445%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fbest-team-won-the-world-cup-gautam-gambhir-slams-bizarre-statement-from-expert-4591445%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fbest-team-won-the-world-cup-gautam-gambhir-slams-bizarre-statement-from-expert-4591445%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20approves%20deal%20to%20free%20around%2050%20hostages%20and%20pause%20war%20with%20Hamas%22%2C%22content%2