%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Uttarkashi%20(Uttarakhand)%20tunnel%20rescue%20%7C%20Sanjeet%20Rana%2C%20a%20cook%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20cooked%20veg%20pulao%2C%20mattar%20paneer%2C%20and%20butter%20chapati%20for%20the%20people%20trapped%20inside.%20We%20have%20packed%20the%20food%20in%20an%20accurate%20portion.%20The%20food%20is%20less%20spicy%20and%20less%20oily...%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FaW6qq3Heyf%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FaW6qq3Heyf%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1726974838106112447%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2021%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Director%20of%20National%20Highways%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20(NHIDCL)%2C%20Anshu%20Manish%20Khulko%2C%20said%20hot%20meals%20such%20as%20Khichdi%20and%20Dalia%20could%20not%20be%20delivered%20in%20cylindrical%20plastic%20bottles%20through%20the%206-inch%20pipe%20as%20something%20got%20stuck%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20now%20we%20have%20cleared%20the%20pipe%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khulko%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20today%20fruits%20such%20as%20oranges%2C%20bananas%20and%20medicines%20were%20supplied%20to%20the%20trapped%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20Ramola%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20hotel%20where%20food%20for%20the%20trapped%20people%20was%20prepared%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20that%20around%20150%20packets%20had%20been%20prepared%20for%20dinner%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20cooked%20food%20for%20those%20trapped%20inside.%20We%20prepared%20rice%20and%20paneer%20today.%20We%20prepared%20about%20150%20packets%20for%20them.%20All%20items%20were%20cooked%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20a%20doctor.%20They%20are%20being%20provided%20with%20easy-to-digest%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramola%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Lt%20Gen%20(Retd)%20Syed%20Ata%20Hasnain%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%2C%20said%20efforts%20to%20rescue%20the%20trapped%20men%20are%20underway%20from%20five%20sides%20but%20the%20best%20possible%20method%20is%20the%20horizontal%20drilling%20by%20the%20Augur%20machine%20from%20the%20Silkyara%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20rescue%20plan%2C%20900%20mm%20pipes%20will%20be%20inserted%20using%20horizontal%20drilling%20equipment%20to%20create%20an%20escape%20route%20for%20the%20trapped%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20additional%20secretary%2C%20Technical%2C%20Road%20and%20Transport%2C%20Mahmood%20Ahmed%2C%20said%20800%20mm-diameter%20pipes%20were%20now%20being%20pushed%20in%20instead%20of%20900%20mm%20through%20the%20telescoping%20method.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20portion%20of%20the%20under-construction%20tunnel%2C%20from%20Silkyara%20to%20Barkot%2C%20caved%20in%20on%20November%2012%2C%20leaving%2041%20labourers%20trapped%20due%20to%20the%20fall%20of%20debris%20in%20a%2060-metre%20stretch%20on%20the%20Silkyara%20side%20of%20the%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDMA%20official%20said%20on%20November%2012%2C%20a%20part%20of%20the%20tunnel%20caved%20in%20trapping%20the%20workers%20inside%20the%202%20km-long%20portion%20of%20the%20tunnel.%20He%20said%20the%20Barkot%20side%20of%20the%20tunnel%20is%20already%20closed%20as%20work%20has%20not%20yet%20begun%20on%20that%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20that%20(Barkot)%20end%20is%20also%20closed.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20workers%20are%20trapped%20between%20the%20caved-in%20portion%20and%20the%20other%20end%20(the%20Barkot%20side)%2C%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20accessed%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Hasnain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20present%2C%20different%20agencies%2C%20NDRF%2C%20ITBP%2C%20Army%20engineers%2C%20SDRF%2C%20fire%20and%20emergency%20services%2C%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%20and%20other%20technical%20agencies%20of%20the%20Central%20government%2C%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20rescue%20operation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDMA%20member%20said%20a%20tunnel%20rescue%20calls%20for%20a%20serious%20and%20challenging%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAround%203-4%20international%20experts%20have%20also%20come%20to%20the%20tunnel%20site.%20The%20government%20has%20flown%20in%20experts%20to%20oversee%20the%20operation%20and%20make%20suggestions%20where%20they%20deem%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Hasnain%20said%20that%20a%20top%20attack%20and%20vertical%20drilling%20to%20pull%20out%20the%20trapped%20labourers%20is%20also%20being%20explored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20that%2C%20the%20Border%20Road%20Organisation%20has%20made%20a%20road%20and%20equipment%20are%20being%20transported%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Hasnain%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20priority%20of%20the%20government%20is%20'life-saving'.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700618580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F3lvvigv4_uttarakhand-tunnel-collapse-meal-for-workers-twitter-ani_625x300_22_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-trapped-workers-get-veg-pulao-matar-paneer-for-dinner-4594195%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20ongoing%20operation%20to%20extricate%2041%20labourers%20trapped%20inside%20the%20collapsed%20portion%20of%20the%20under-construction%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20entered%20its%20tenth%20day%2C%20rescuers%20on%20Tuesday%20packed%20solid%20food%20items%20such%20as%20veg%20pulao%20and%20matar%20paneer%20for%20dinner.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUr