0including%20about%2040%20children%2C%20elderly%20people%20and%20dozens%20of%20Thai%20and%20Nepali%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hostage%20deal%20will%20include%20the%20release%20of%20some%20150%20to%20300%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20in%20Israel%2C%20among%20them%20female%20and%20minor%20prisoners%2C%20The%20Times%20of%20Israel%20reported%20citing%20Channel%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChannel%2012%20stated%20further%20that%20the%20hostage%20releases%20could%20begin%20on%20Thursday%20or%20Friday.%20The%20report%20says%20the%20ceasefire%20could%20be%20extended%20to%20allow%20the%20release%20of%20more%20hostages%20following%20the%20initial%2050%20or%20so.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIsraeli%20Defence%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20said%20his%20country%20will%20need%20to%20make%20%26quot%3Bdifficult%20decisions%26quot%3B%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20hostages%20held%20by%20the%20Hamas%20terror%20group%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20moving%20step%20by%20step%20towards%20the%20total%20defeat%20of%20Hamas%20and%20getting%20closer%20to%20bringing%20the%20hostages%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Gallant%20said%20following%20an%20assessment%20with%20military%20officials%20at%20the%20Gaza%20Division%20base%20in%20southern%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20will%20all%20have%20to%20make%20difficult%2C%20important%20decisions%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20not%20a%20moment%20throughout%20this%20campaign--45%20days--that%20I%20don't%20think%20about%20the%20hostages%2C%26quot%3B%20Gallant%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20X%2C%20depicting%20the%20reasons%20behind%20Hamas%20supposedly%20using%20the%20Shifa%20Hospital%20as%20a%20place%20to%20hold%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20shared%20video%20was%20a%20text%20that%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20WHY%20Hamas%20brought%20hostages%20to%20the%20Shifa%20Hospital%20after%20the%20October%207%20massacre.%20Why%20is%20Hamas%20still%20holding%20over%20200%20civilians%20hostage%2044%20days%20later%3F%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20military%20wing%20of%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%20declared%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20question%20the%20world%20should%20be%20asking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%207%2C%20Hamas%20conducted%20an%20offensive%20operation%20into%20Israel%2C%20reportedly%20rebelling%20against%20the%20Israeli%20regime.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20the%20group%20took%20over%20200%20people%20hostage%2C%20transporting%20them%20into%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20the%20IDF%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BThousands%20of%20Hamas%20terrorists%20invaded%20Israel%2C%20amidst%20their%20massacre%2C%20they%20abducted%20over%20200%20innocent%20people%20and%20brought%20them%20into%20Gaza%20by%20brute%20force.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20World%20Children's%20Day%2C%20Israel%20shared%20pictures%20of%20children%20held%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%20terrorists%20in%20Gaza%2C%20stressing%20that%20there%20are%20more%20than%2030%20children%2C%20including%20babies%20and%20toddlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20further%20urged%20the%20international%20community%20to%20take%20action%20to%20bring%20them%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20your%20children%20are%20at%20school%2C%20there%20are%20currently%20more%20than%2030%20Israeli%20babies%2C%20toddlers%20and%20children%20being%20held%20hostage%20in%20Gaza%20by%20Hamas%20terrorists.%20On%20%23WorldChildrensDay%20we%20demand%20action%20from%20the%20international%20community.%20BRING%20OUR%20CHILDREN%20HOME!%2C%26quot%3B%20Israel%20shared%20the%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20post%2C%20they%20shared%20the%20images%20of%20these%20children%20and%20emphasised%20that%20these%20children%20should%20be%20with%20their%20families%20and%20not%20in%20a%20dark%20room%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20each%20and%20every%20one%20of%20their%20faces.%20These%20are%20the%20babies%2C%20toddlers%20and%20children%20being%20held%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%20terrorists%20in%20Gaza.%20They%20should%20be%20with%20their%20families.%20Not%20in%20a%20dark%20room%20somewhere%20in%20Gaza.%20BRING%20THEM%20HOME!%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700591520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F4dk2bkj4_israeli-hostages-posters-at-embassy-_625x300_02_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-could-free-50-hostages-in-4-5-days-in-deal-with-israel-report-4594379%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Israeli%20Cabinet%20will%20meet%20at%208%20pm%20(Israeli%20local%20time)%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20approve%20a%20deal%20for%20the%20release%20of%20dozens%20of%20hostages%20from%20Gaza%2C%20The%20Times%20of%20Israel%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-could-free-50-hostages-in-4-5-days-in-deal-with-israel-report-4594379%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-could-free-50-hostages-in-4-5-days-in-deal-with-israel-report-4594379%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-could-free-50-hostages-in-4-5-days-in-deal-with-israel-report-4594379%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CEO%20of%20world's%20largest%20crypto%20exchange%20steps%20down%20-%20and%20pleads%20guilty%20to%20criminal%20charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700591040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F22%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-binance-crypto-cryptocurrency_5681165.jpg%3F20220221134216%22%2C%22originID%