nesia%20gives%20hundreds%20of%20rejected%20Rohingya%20temporary%20stay%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700589950000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105395090%2Cimgsize-1538378.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Findonesia-gives-hundreds-of-rejected-rohingya-temporary-stay%2Farticleshow%2F105395071.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105395071.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EHundreds%20of%20Rohingya%20refugees%20in%20Indonesia%20have%20been%20given%20shelter%20for%20three%20months%20following%20threats%20from%20locals%20to%20turn%20them%20back%20to%20sea.%20The%20group%20of%20256%20refugees%2C%20who%20had%20been%20turned%20back%20twice%20before%20successfully%20making%20land%20on%20their%20third%20attempt%2C%20were%20initially%20held%20in%20a%20temporary%20shelter.%20They%20have%20now%20been%20relocated%20to%20a%20new%20shelter%20in%20Lhokseumawe.%20The%20refugees%20will%20be%20provided%20with%20security%20during%20their%20temporary%20stay%2C%20but%20no%20details%20were%20given%20about%20their%20future%20after%20the%20three%20months%20expires.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Findonesia-gives-hundreds-of-rejected-rohingya-temporary-stay%2Farticleshow%2F105395071.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Findonesia-gives-hundreds-of-rejected-rohingya-temporary-stay%2Famp_articleshow%2F105395071.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Findonesia-gives-hundreds-of-rejected-rohingya-temporary-stay%2Famp_articleshow%2F105395071.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAbsolutely%20Inhuman%26quot%3B%3A%20Manipur%20MLA%20On%20Highway%20Blockade%20In%20Crisis-Hit%20State%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20killing%20of%20two%20men%20in%20Manipur's%20Kangpokpi%20district%20yesterday%20by%20suspected%20insurgents%20had%20led%20to%20a%20shutdown%20call%2C%20including%20the%20blocking%20of%20National%20Highway%202%2C%20by%20an%20organisation%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EValley-based%20civil%20society%20groups%20have%2C%20however%2C%20criticised%20the%20move%20to%20block%20the%20highway%20as%20punishing%20an%20entire%20population%20over%20the%20action%20of%20armed%20miscreants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur's%20lifelines%20that%20pass%20through%20hill%20areas%20are%20the%20first%20casualty%20whenever%20local%20tensions%20arise%3B%20they%20are%20immediately%20blocked%20-%20sometimes%20for%20months%20-%20by%20any%20group%20to%20use%20as%20a%20leverage%20for%20their%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20two%20men%2C%20Henminlen%20Vaiphei%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20on%20Monday%2C%20served%20in%20the%20Indian%20Reserve%20Battalion.%20Unidentified%20armed%20assailants%20ambushed%20them%20while%20they%20were%20travelling%20in%20a%20Maruti%20Gypsy%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOn%2020.11.2023%2C%20at%20Khonsakhul-L.%20Munlai%20Junction%2C%20Kangpokpi%2C%20two%20individuals%2C%20including%20one%20police%20personnel%20of%206th%20IRB%20namely%20Henminlen%20Vaiphei%2C%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20an%20ambush%20by%20unidentified%20armed%20assailants%20while%20traveling%20in%20a%20Maruti%20Gypsy.%20Security%20forces%20immediately%20launched...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Manipur%20Police%20(%40manipur_police)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanipur_police%2Fstatus%2F1726638606956351674%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20Kangpokpi-based%20Committee%20on%20Tribal%20Unity%20(COTU)%20in%20a%20statement%20announced%20the%20%26quot%3Bemergency%20shutdown%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20district%20where%20one%20of%20the%20lifelines%20of%20Manipur%20passes%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20We%20are%20no%20longer%20safe%20under%20the%20partisan%20government...%20The%20meeting%20calls%20for%20an%20early%20materialisation%20of%20the%20demand%20for%20separation%20from%20Manipur...%20Political%20separation%20is%20the%20only%20option%20left%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Kangpokpi%20group%20that%20represents%20the%20hill-majority%20Kuki%20tribes%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20(ITLF)%2C%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKangpokpi%20is%2045%20km%20from%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%2C%20the%20valley%20area%20where%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20Meiteis%20live.%20Both%20communities%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20ethnic%20clashes%20since%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur's%20independent%20MLA%20Nishikant%20Singh%20Sapam%2C%20condemning%20the%20sudden%20highway%20blockade%2C%20told%20NDTV%20only%20two%20highways%20connect%20the%20state%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bimposing%20a%20blockade%20on%20these%20lifelines%20by%20anyone%20is%20similar%20to%20choking%20a%20person%20by%20the%20neck%20and%20threatening%20their%20survival%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20absolutely%20inhuman%2C%20totally%20unlawful.%20Essential%20items%20reach%20in%20trickles%20with%20great%20difficulty%2C%20leading%20to%20price%20rise%2C%20making%20survival%20a%20lot%20more%20difficult%20to%20the%20already%20difficult%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%20This%20practice%20(of%20blocking%20highways)%20must%20stop.%20It's%20cruelty%20to%20an%20extreme%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Sapam%2C%20who%20is%20based%20in%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F5gl7kf2g_manipur-generic-debanish-credit_625x300_21_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighway%20blockades%20in%20Manipur%20add%20more%20burden%20to%20transporters%20and%20eventually%20the%20consumers%20due%20to%20daylight%20extortion%20that%20operates%20as%20an%20open%20secret.%20NDTV%20on%20September%2015%20reported%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fillegal-highway-tax-hawala-and-price-rise-are-manipurs-biggest-silent-problem-4393522%5C%22%3Ecost%20of%20illegal%20highway%20'tax'%3C%2Fa%3E%20extorted%20from%20truck%20drivers%20in%20Manipur%20is%20passed%20on%20to%20consumers%20in%20the%20ethnic%20violence-hit%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prices%20of%20essentials%20and%20other%20goods%20have%20risen%20between%2010%20per%20cent%20and%2030%20per%20cent%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20item.%20Fruit%20and%20fish%20cost%2050%20per%20cent%20more%20in%20Manipur%2C%20compared%20to%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ethnic%20unrest%20in%20Manipur%20began%20on%20May%203%20following%20a%20protest%20by%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20against%20the%20Meiteis'%20demand%20for%20inclusion%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20category.%20Though%20the%20immediate%20cause%20of%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20is%20said%20to%20be%20over%20the%20Meities'%20demand%20for%20ST%20tag%2C%20many%20leaders%20including%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20have%20said%20entry%20of%20illegal%20immigrants%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20factors%20behind%20the%20unrest%20in%20the%20northeast%20state%2C%20which%20is%20ruled%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20anti-terror%20body%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20has%20said%20it%20is%20looking%20into%20an%20alleged%20