%20(PMLA)%20against%20the%20newspaper%E2%80%99s%20publisher%C2%A0Associated%20Journals%20Ltd%20(AJL)%20and%20its%20holding%20company%20Young%20Indian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInvestigation%20revealed%20that%20M%2Fs.%20Associated%20Journals%20Ltd.%20(AJL)%20is%20in%20possession%20of%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20in%20the%20form%20of%20immovable%20properties%20spread%20across%20many%20cities%20of%20India%20such%20as%20Delhi%2C%C2%A0Mumbai%C2%A0and%C2%A0Lucknow%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs.%20661.69%20Crore%20and%20M%2Fs.%20Young%20Indian%20(YI)%20is%20in%20possession%20of%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs.%2090.21%20Crore%20in%20the%20form%20of%20investment%20in%20equity%20shares%20of%20AJL%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ED%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20responding%20to%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20statement%2C%20said%20the%20probe%20agency%E2%80%99s%20actions%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20was%20panicking%20about%20the%20ongoing%20state%20assembly%20elections.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20pattern%20of%20misuse%20of%20agencies%20during%20elections%20by%20the%20BJP%20establishment%20is%20not%20new%20and%20now%20stands%20fully%20exposed%20before%20the%20entire%20nation.%20National%20Herald%20was%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20Freedom%20Movement.%20The%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20is%20proud%20of%20its%20role%20in%20the%20Freedom%20Movement%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EReports%20of%20attachment%20of%20AJL%E2%80%99s%20properties%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20are%20a%20clear%20indication%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20panic%20in%20the%20ongoing%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStaring%20at%20defeat%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Mizoram%2C%20the%20BJP%20Govt%20feels%20compelled%20to%20misuse%20its%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FpnJYnVartI%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FpnJYnVartI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20(%40kharge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%2Fstatus%2F1726989795086209501%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2021%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fexplainer-why-has-the-ed-summoned-the-gandhis-in-the-national-herald-case%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0is%20an%20English%20newspaper%20which%20was%20started%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20along%20with%20a%20company%20called%20the%20Associated%20Journals%20Limited%20(AJL).%20The%20company%20published%20newspapers%20in%20two%20languages%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3Cem%3EQaumi%20Awaz%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0in%20Urdu%20and%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENavjeevan%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0in%20Hindi.%20Post%20independence%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENational%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0was%20known%20for%20supporting%20the%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%201%2C%202012%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20leader%20Subramanian%20Swamy%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fnews%2Fexplainers%2Fwhat-is-national-herald-case-rahul-sonia-gandhi-ed-congress-5360941.html%5C%22%3E%C2%A0filed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%20case%20against%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20alleging%20that%20they%20have%20used%20party%20funds%20to%20purchase%20the%20company%20that%20published%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENational%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper.%20In%20his%20complaint%20before%20a%20trial%20court%20in%20Delhi%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20has%20committed%20fraud%20and%20grabbed%20land%20of%20about%20thousands%20of%20crores.%20He%20further%20claimed%20that%20the%20Gandhis%20%E2%80%9Cfraudulently%20acquired%20properties%20of%20Associated%20Journals%20Ltd%20(AJL)%20in%20Delhi%2C%20UP%2C%20and%20other%20places%20worth%20Rs%201%2C600%20crore%E2%80%9D%20through%20the%20private%20company%20Young%20Indian%20Ltd%2C%20which%20they%20owned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20then%20registered%20a%20case%20in%202021%2C%20to%20interrogate%20alleged%20financial%20irregularities%20at%20Young%20India%20Ltd%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20the%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA).%20This%20came%20as%20a%20result%20of%20a%20trial%20court%20taking%20cognisance%20of%20an%20income%20tax%20department%20probe%20against%20Young%20India%20Ltd%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20complaint%20made%20by%20Swamy%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700588201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29180215%2FThe-Wire-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fnational-herald-case-ed-attaches-properties-worth-rs-751-9-crore-congress-calls-it-election-panic%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThis%20pattern%20of%20misuse%20of%20agencies%20during%20elections%20by%20the%20BJP%20establishment%20is%20not%20new%20and%20now%20stands%20fully%20exposed%20before%20the%20entire%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fnational-herald-case-ed-attaches-properties-worth-rs-751-9-crore-congress-calls-it-election-panic%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Niger's%20junta%20asks%20West%20Africa's%20court%20to%20compel%20neighbours%20to%20lift%20coup%20sanctions%2C%20citing%20hardship%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700588019000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105394752%2Cimgsize-1197974.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fnigers-junta-asks-west-africas-court-to-compel-neighbours-to-lift-coup-sanctions-citing-hardship