Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%2C%20on%20August%2023%2C%202022%2C%20had%20issued%20notices%20to%20the%20Union%20health%20ministry%20and%20Ministry%20of%20Ayush%20and%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20Ltd%2C%20on%20the%20plea%20of%20the%20IMA%20alleging%20a%20smear%20campaign%20by%20Ramdev%20against%20the%20vaccination%20drive%20and%20modern%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20brief%20hearing%2C%20the%20bench%20asked%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20not%20to%20publish%20misleading%20claims%20and%20advertisements%20against%20modern%20systems%20of%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20bench%20may%20also%20consider%20imposing%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20on%20every%20product%20if%20a%20false%20claim%20is%20made%20that%20it%20can%20cure%20a%20particular%20ailment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20asked%20the%20counsel%20appearing%20for%20the%20Centre%20to%20find%20a%20remedy%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20misleading%20medical%20advertisements%20where%20claims%20are%20being%20made%20about%20medicines%20that%20offer%20perfect%20cure%20of%20certain%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20will%20now%20take%20up%20the%20plea%20of%20IMA%20for%20hearing%20on%20February%205%2C%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%2C%20while%20issuing%20notices%20on%20the%20plea%2C%20had%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20Ramdev%20for%20criticising%20allopathy%20and%20allopathic%20practitioners%2C%20saying%20he%20needed%20to%20be%20restrained%20from%20abusing%20the%20doctors%20and%20other%20systems%20of%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happened%20to%20this%20Guru%20Swami%20Ramdev%20Baba%3F...%20Ultimately%20we%20respect%20him%20as%20he%20popularised%20yoga.%20We%20all%20go%20for%20this.%20But%2C%20he%20should%20not%20criticise%20the%20other%20system.%20What%20is%20the%20guarantee%20that%20Ayurveda%20whatever%20system%20he%20is%20following%20will%20work%3F%20You%20see%20the%20type%20of%20advertisements%20accusing%20all%20the%20doctors%20as%20if%20they%20are%20killers%20or%20something.%20Huge%20advertisements%20(have%20been%20given)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20headed%20by%20the%20then%20CJI%20NV%20Ramana%2C%20since%20retired%2C%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIMA%20had%20referred%20to%20several%20advertisements%20which%20allegedly%20projected%20the%20allopath%20and%20the%20doctors%20in%20poor%20light%2C%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bdisparaging%26quot%3B%20statements%20have%20also%20been%20made%20by%20firms%2C%20engaged%20in%20the%20production%20of%20ayurvedic%20medicines%2C%20to%20mislead%20the%20general%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20commercials%20say%20that%20the%20medical%20practitioners%20themselves%20are%20dying%20despite%20taking%20modern%20medicines%2C%20the%20counsel%20for%20the%20IMA%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIMA%20had%20said%20that%20a%20concerted%20effort%20was%20being%20made%20to%20discourage%20the%20vaccinations%2C%20including%20the%20COVID-19%20jab%20drive%2C%20and%20the%20use%20of%20allopathic%20medicines%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700587800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-05%2F9n2b4ps4_ramdev-pti_625x300_22_May_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupeme-court-pulls-up-ramdevs-patanjali-stop-false-advertisements-immediately-4594149%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20Tuesday%20cautioned%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%2C%20a%20company%20co-founded%20by%20yoga%20guru%20Ramdev%20and%20dealing%20in%20herbal%20products%2C%20against%20making%20%26quot%3Bfalse%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%26quot%3B%20claims%20in%20advertisements%20about%20its%20medicines%20as%20cure%20of%20several%20diseases.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fin