html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Want%20A%20Region%20Where%20Sovereignty%20Is%20Respected%3A%20Australian%20Minister%20On%20Quad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Quad%20is%20crucial%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20power%20balance%20in%20southeast%20Asia%20and%20the%20growing%20partnership%20with%20India%20is%20important%20in%20terms%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bshared%20view%26quot%3B%20about%20what%20happens%20in%20the%20region%2C%20Australian%20foreign%20minister%20Penny%20Wong%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Australia%2C%20she%20said%2C%20share%20%26quot%3Bdemocratic%20traditions%2C%20which%20we%20value%2C%20democratic%20institutions%2C%20which%20we%20value%2C%20and%20interests%20about%20the%20sort%20of%20region%20we%20want%20to%20live%20in...%20it%20is%20peaceful%2C%20stable%20and%20prosperous%2C%20a%20region%20where%20sovereignty%20is%20respected%2C%20and%20so%20we're%20working%20together%20to%20ensure%20that%20occurs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20Australia%20sees%20its%20relationship%20with%20China%20as%20opposed%20to%20Quad%2C%20often%20seen%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Banti-China%20alliance%26quot%3B%2C%20Ms%20Wong%20--%20who%20is%20in%20Delhi%20for%20the%20second%20India-Australia%202%2B2%20Ministerial%20Dialogues%20--%20said%20Australia%20will%20continue%20to%20engage%20with%20China%20and%20disagree%20where%20it%20is%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Quad%2C%20she%20said%2C%20is%20a%20group%20of%20countries%20who%20are%20looking%20to%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20is%20happening%20in%20our%20region%2C%20looking%20to%20deliver%20value%20to%20the%20countries%20of%20the%20region%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20countries%20which%20do%20have%20a%20shared%20view%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20international%20system%2C%20the%20international%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20trading%20arrangements%20which%20are%20transparent%20and%20fair.%20And%20it%20is%20a%20good%20thing%20that%20we%20work%20together%20and%20it's%20a%20very%20important%20partnership%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuad%2C%20a%20four-nation%20alliance%20of%20US%2C%20Japan%2C%20Australia%20and%20India%2C%20was%20revived%20in%202017%20and%20one%20of%20its%20key%20drivers%20was%20China's%20growing%20assertiveness%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%20India%20is%20seen%20by%20a%20section%20as%20a%20possible%20counterweight%20to%20China%2C%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20economy%20and%20geo-politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20China's%20role%20in%20the%20region%2C%20Ms%20Wong%20said%20Australia%20focuses%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bimportance%20of%20the%20observance%20of%20international%20law%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAustralia%20is%20a%20middle%20power.%20We%20rely%20greatly%20on%20the%20international%20system.%20So%20when%20we%20look%20at%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20or%20training%20arrangements%2C%20what%20we%20see%20is%20the%20importance%20of%20countries%20like%20India%20and%20Australia%20asserting%20that%20rules%20which%20have%20been%20agreed%20norms%20which%20have%20been%20agreed%20are%20observe%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20meet%20of%20Quad%20is%20due%20in%20January.%20There%20are%20hopes%20that%20trade%20talks%20between%20India%20and%20Australia%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20matter%2C%20Ms%20Wong%20said%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bbit%20of%20work%20to%20do%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20already%20have%20an%20agreement%20between%20our%20two%20countries%2C%20which%2C%20provides%20a%20lot%20of%20tariff%20free%20engagement%2C%20tariff%20free%20trade%E2%80%A6%20It%20is%20going%20to%20take%20work%20from%20both%20sides....%20(which%20have%20to)%20deal%20with%20some%20of%20the%20sensitive%20issues%20in%20their%20own%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700582700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F9ge01ba4_penny-wong_625x300_21_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwant-a-region-where-sovereignty-is-respected-australian-minister-penny-wong-on-role-of-quad-4593752%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Quad%20is%20crucial%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20power%20balance%20in%20southeast%20Asia%20and%20the%20growing%20partnership%20with%20India%20is%20important%20in%20terms%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bshared%20view%26quot%3B%20about%20what%20happens%20in%20the%20region%2C%20Australian%20foreign%20minister%20Penny%20Wong%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20int%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwant-a-region-where-sovereignty-is-respected-australian-minister-penny-wong-on-role-of-quad-4593752%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwant-a-region-where-sovereignty-is-respected-australian-minister-penny-wong-on-role-of-quad-4593752%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwant-a-region-where-sovereignty-is-respected-australian-minister-penny-wong-on-role-of-quad-4593752%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ganapati%20Becomes%20a%20New%20Flashpoint%20in%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20Politics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21212822%2FIMG-20231121-WA02481.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBengaluru%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20November%202%2C%20a%20prominent%20Lingayat%20swami%20asked%20his%20community%20to%20stop%20worshipping%20Ganapati%20and%20unwittingly%20set%20off%20a%20huge%20controversy.%20%E2%80%9CGanapati%20is%20not%20Lingayat%20culture.%20Instead%20of%20starting%20events%20with%20a%20prayer%20to%20him%2C%20Lingayats%20should%20sing%20Vachanas%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Panditaradhya%20Shivacharya%20Swami%20of%20the%20Sanehalli%20matha%20in%20Chitradurga%20district%20of%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVachanas%2C%20simple%20prose-poems%20composed%20by%20founding%20fathers%20of%20the%20Lingayat%20movement%2C%20are%20the%20religious%20scriptures%20of%20the%20community.%20Lingayats%20are%20descendants%20of%20a%20band%20of%20reformers%20led%20by%20Basavanna%2C%20who%20rejected%20Vedic%20norms%20and%20tried%20to%20form%20an%20egalitarian%2C%20inclusive%20society%20in%2012th-century%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20largely%20working%20class%20movement%2C%20which%20drew%20members%20from%20all%20castes%2C%20was%20crushed%20by%20the%20establishment%20and%20the%20tragic%20memory%20is%20burnt%20into%20the%20Lingayat%20mind.%20Basavanna%E2%80%99s%20emotional%20appeal%20cuts%20across%20caste%20and%20religion%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20several%20backward%20groups%20in%20Karnataka%20trace%20their%20social%20origin%20to%20the%2012th-century%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20over%20the%20centuries%20Lingayats%20have%20relapsed%20into%20many%20Hindu%20practices%2C%20a%20small%20but%20influential%20section%20of%20them%20is%20seeking%20to%20revive%20the%20distinct%20radical%20ethos%20of%20the%20founding%20movement%20and%20claim%20a%20separate%20religious%20status%20for%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPanditaradhya%20swami%20along%20with%20many%20other%20Lingayat%20religious%20leaders%20have%20opposed%20the%20worship%20of%20Hindu%20gods%20by%20the%20community%20for%20decades.%20Many%20of%20them%20routinely%20persuade%20their%20followers%20to%20empty%20their%20homes%20of%20idols%20and%20photos%20of%20Hindu%20gods.%20But%20for%20some%20reason%20the%20November%202%20statement%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20Hindutva%20advocates%2C%20who%20decided%20to%20go%20after%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20police%20complaint%20was%20filed%20for%20hurting%20religious%20sentiments%2C%20TV%20channels%20gave%20the%20controversy%20breathless%20coverage%2C%20and%20a%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E-affiliated%20Kannada%20newspaper%20ran%20a%20continuous%20campaign%20for%20nine%20days%20publishing%20as%20many%20as%2012%20reports%20on%20the%20issue%20either%20on%20the%20front%20page%20or%20on%20the%20opinion%20page%20or%20on%20both.%20They%20asked%20him%20to%20apologise%20for%20%E2%80%9Coffending%E2%80%9D%20the%20Sanatani%20religion%20and%20respect%20the%20plural%20nature%20of%20Indian%20society.%20One%20report%20spoke%20of%20an%20internationally%20funded%20conspiracy%20to%20undermine%20Hinduism.%20He%20was%20described%20as%20%E2%80%98shameless%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98mentally%20disturbed%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98lefty%2C%E2%80%99%20and%20a%20%E2%80%98Naxal%E2%80%99%20in%20these%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22How%20Karnataka's%20Lingayat%20Community%20was%20First%20Hinduised%20and%20Then%20Hindutvaised%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkarnataka-election-lingayat-hindutva%5C%22%3EHow%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20Lingayat%20Community%20was%20First%20Hinduised%20and%20Then%20Hindutvaised%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPanditaradhya%20swami%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20progressive%20religious%20leader%20as%20he%20often%20asks%20his%20followers%20to%20grow%20a%20scientific%20temper%2C%20reject%20astrology%20and%20stop%20accepting%20puranas%20as%20gospels.%20He%20takes%20up%20the%20causes%20of%20weaker%20sections%20and%20enjoys%20a%20large%20following%20outside%20Lingayats.%20He%20has%20been%20organising%20a%20popular%20theatre%20festival%20every%20year%20for%20decades%20in%20which%20socially%20sensitive%20plays%20are%20prioritised.%20He%20is%20a%20strong%20advocate%20for%20a%20separate%20Lingayat%20religion%20and%20bringing%20back%20Basavanna%E2%80%99s%20teachings%20is%20the%20central%20theme%20of%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20media%20campaign%20against%20him%20started%2C%20Lingayat%20groups%20interpreted%20it%20as%20an%20Hindutva%20attack%20on%20Basava%20philosophy%20and%20came%20out%20in%20support.%20Former%20IAS%20officer%20S.M.%20Jamdar%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20Lingayats%20especially%20Veerashaivas%20worship%20Hindu%20gods%20due%20to%20the%20influence%20of%20their%20neighbours.%20The%20Swamiji%20was%20right%20in%20questioning%20them.%E2%80%9D%20Jamdar%20is%20the%20secretary%20of%20Jagathika%20Lingayata%20Mahasabha%20(JLM)%2C%20which%20is%20spearheading%20the%20fight%20for%20a%20separate%20Lingayat%20religion.%20He%20says%20the%20swami%E2%80%99s%20comments%20were%20made%20at%20a%20Lingayat%20function%20and%20were%20for%20Lingayats%20only.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20need%20for%20others%20to%20get%20upset.%20We%20condemn%20the%20intemperate%20attack%20on%20him%20in%20equally%20strong%20words%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20older%20and%20more%20resourceful%20community%20organisation%20All%20India%20Veerashaiva%20Mahasabha%20(AIVM)%20refrained%20from%20issuing%20a%20public%20statement%20but%20indicated%20they%20were%20with%20the%20swami.%20Its%20secretary%20Renuka%20Prasanna%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%20The%20swamiji%20spoke%20the%20truth%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20start%20any%20programme%20with%20a%20Ganapati%20prayer.%20There%20is%20no%20question%20of%20not%20supporting%20him%2C%20if%20required%20we%20will%20also%20hit%20the%20streets.%E2%80%9D%20AIVM%20is%20more%20conservative%2C%20ambivalent%20on%20a%20separate%20Lingayat%20religion%20and%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20the%20JLM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20campaign%20against%20Panditaradhya%20swami%2C%20Lingayat%20groups%20staged%20sporadic%20protests%2C%20launched%20a%20counter%20media%20campaign%20and%20started%20flooding%20social%20media%20with%20explicitly%20anti-Vedic%20Vachanas.%20Many%20left-leaning%20progressive%20activists%20also%20joined%20in%20and%20on%20November%2022%2C%20both%20groups%20are%20coming%20together%20to%20support%20the%20swami%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Bangalore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%20six%20well%20known%20Lingayat%20religious%20leaders%20came%20out%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Panditaradhya%20swami.%20The%20lone%20exception%20was%20Dr%20Shivamurthy%20Shivacharya%20Swami%20of%20the%20powerful%20Sirigere%20matha%2C%20who%20opposed%20%E2%80%98fundamentalists%E2%80%99%20and%20said%20there%20was%20nothing%20in%20Vachanas%20that%20went%20against%20Vedas.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Sirigere%20Swamiji%20happens%20to%20be%20Panditaradhya%20swamiji%E2%80%99s%20senior%20in%20the%20matha%20hierarchy%20and%20has%20been%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20his%20junior%20for%20years.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20he%20is%20using%20this%20opportunity%20to%20settle%20scores%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jamdar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20right%20to%20pick%20a%20few%20Vachanas%20selectively%20and%20misinterpret%20them.%20It%20was%20not%20just%20Basavanna%E2%80%A6Many%20like%20Allama%20Prabhu%2C%20Siddarama%2C%20Ambigara%20Chowdaiah%20rejected%20Vedas%20without%20mincing%20words%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jamdar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22In%20Lingayat-Veerashaiva%20Row%2C%20a%20History%20of%20Dissent%20and%20Assimilation%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Flingayat-viraishaiva-hinduism-religion%5C%22%3EIn%20Lingayat-Veerashaiva%20Row%2C%20a%20History%20of%20Dissent%20and%20Assimilation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relationship%20between%20Lingayats%20and%20Hinduism%20is%20long%20debated.%20Though%20usually%20seen%20as%20a%20Shaivite%20community%2C%20the%20Lingayat%20Shiva%20does%20not%20reside%20in%20Kailasa%20nor%20is%20he%20married%20to%20Parvati%20or%20is%20the%20creator%20of%20Ganesha.%20He%20is%20a%20formless%20divine%20energy%20that%20is%20manifest%20in%20the%20Ishtalinga%2C%20which%20Lingayats%20carry%20and%20worship.%20Though%20Lingayat%20beliefs%20prohibit%20polytheism%2C%20most%20people%20in%20the%20community%20do%20exactly%20that%20and%20the%20groups%20fighting%20for%20separate%20religion%20are%20locked%20in%20a%20constant%20battle%20to%20discourage%20the%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ganapati%20controversy%20that%20has%20grabbed%20headlines%20for%20nearly%20two%20weeks%20in%20Karnataka%20underlines%20the%20challenges%20before%20the%20Hindutva%20advocates%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20the%20May%202023%20state%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20slumped%20from%20104%20to%2066%20MLAs%20%E2%80%93%20and%20not%20just%20due%20to%20bad%20governance%20and%20inflation.%20It%20also%20ran%20into%20tough%20ideological%20opposition%20from%20Muslims%2C%20Dalits%2C%20many%20backward%20castes%20and%20the%20JLM%20Lingayats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dissent%20of%20Lingayats%20is%20probably%20more%20damaging%20for%20the%20BJP%20as%20the%20community%20constitutes%20its%20primary%20vote%20bank.%20J.S.%20Patil%2C%20a%20full-time%20JLM%20activist%2C%20points%20out%20that%20while%20Lingayats%20may%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%20is%20largely%20due%20to%20political%20expediency%20rather%20than%20any%20ideological%20commitment.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20always%20aware%20that%20we%20are%20in%20an%20intense%20power%20struggle%20with%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20within%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Hindutva%20advocates%20may%20see%20the%20Ganapati%20controversy%20as%20an%20existential%20threat%2C%20Lingayat%20activists%20see%20it%20as%20an%20opportunity.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20thank%20Hindutva%20groups%20with%20folded%20hands%20for%20creating%20this%20controversy%20and%20energising%20us.%20We%20need%20one%20controversy%20like%20this%20every%20year%20to%20keep%20our%20fight%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Prasanna%20Alanahalli%2C%20an%20activist%20in%20Mysuru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EM.A.%20Arun%20is%20a%20Bangalore-based%20writer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700582598000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21212822%2FIMG-20231121-WA02481.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Flingayat-karnataka-hindutva-ganapati%22%2C%