%20He%20also%20urged%20the%20international%20community%20to%20prevent%20further%20escalation%20and%20stabilize%20the%20Middle%20East.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fxi-jinping-calls-for-ceasefire-to-end-israel-hamas-conflict-in-gaza%2Farticleshow%2F105393276.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Infant%20Branded%20With%20Hot%20Bangles%20By%20Faith%20Healer%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20month-old%20boy%20was%20branded%20with%20hot%20bangles%20all%20over%20his%20body%20by%20a%20faith%20healer%20to%20cure%20him%20of%20pneumonia%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20police%20said%20today.%20The%20incident%20occurred%20earlier%20this%20month%20in%20Hardi%20village%20in%20Shahdol%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%20is%20now%20undergoing%20treatment%20at%20a%20government%20hospital%20while%20the%20police%20have%20charged%20his%20mother%20and%20grandfather%2C%20and%20the%20'dai'%20Booti%20Bai%20Baiga%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2040%20scars%20were%20found%20on%20the%20boy's%20neck%2C%20stomach%20and%20other%20body%20parts%2C%20said%20doctors%20who%20are%20treating%20him.%20He%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%20after%20his%20condition%20deteriorated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20now%20stable%20and%20on%20oxygen%20support%20at%20the%20paediatric%20intensive%20care%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20practice%20of%20'daagna'%20prevalent%20among%20the%20tribals%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20involves%20superstitious%20healing%20methods%2C%20which%20includes%20branding%20infants%20suffering%20from%20pneumonia%20with%20hot%20objects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy's%20family%20had%20approached%20the%20'dai'%2C%20referred%20to%20women%20who%20work%20as%20traditional%20birth%20attendants%2C%20allegedly%20for%20the%20treatment%20of%20pneumonia.%20Booti%20Bai%20Baiga%20then%20branded%20the%20b