%3EAt%20a%20media%20briefing%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Jaishankar%20confirmed%20that%20the%20Canadian%20issue%20was%20raised%20during%20the%20talks%20with%20his%20Australian%20counterpart%2C%20Penny%20Wong%2C%20who%20was%20also%20in%20Delhi%20to%20attend%20the%20%E2%80%982%20plus%202%E2%80%99%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20Australia%20had%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20strong%20relationship%E2%80%9D%20with%20both%20India%20and%20Canada%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20it%20was%20important%20that%20Australia%20get%20our%20perspective%20on%20the%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20our%20point%20of%20view%2C%20the%20key%20issue%20is%20really%20the%20space%20which%20is%20being%20given%20to%20extremism%20and%20radicalism%20in%20Canada%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralian%20foreign%20minister%20Penny%20Wong%20said%20that%20she%20had%20listened%20to%20Jaishankar%E2%80%99s%20perspective%2C%20but%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20repeat%20Canberra%E2%80%99s%20position.%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20point%20to%20my%20previous%20comments%20on%20this%20matter%20on%20which%20I%20have%20responded%20on%20a%20number%20of%20occasions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelations%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20nose-dived%20after%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20went%20public%20with%20a%20potential%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20agents%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Canadian%20citizen%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20on%20June%2018%20in%20British%20Columbia.%20India%20considers%20Nijjar%20to%20be%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20firmly%20dismissed%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20claims%20as%20%E2%80%9Cabsurd%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmotivated%E2%80%9D.%20India%20and%20Canada%20expelled%20a%20senior%20diplomat%20each%20in%20a%20tit-for-tat%20measure.%20Besides%2C%20India%20also%20stopped%20all%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadians%2C%20which%20was%20partially%20resumed%20earlier%20this%20month.%20Additionally%2C%20India%20enforced%20%E2%80%9Cp