ckstone-to-close-multi-strategy-fund-after-assets-drop-nearly-90-123112100953_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US-based%20asset%20manager%20said%20it%20had%20informed%20clients%20after%20it%20decided%20in%20October%20that%20its%20Blackstone%20Diversified%20Multi-Strategy%20fund%20would%20close%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fblackstone-to-close-multi-strategy-fund-after-assets-drop-nearly-90-123112100953_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fblackstone-to-close-multi-strategy-fund-after-assets-drop-nearly-90-123112100953_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fblackstone-to-close-multi-strategy-fund-after-assets-drop-nearly-90-123112100953_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congo-Brazzaville%20stampede%3A%20Dozens%20killed%20during%20army%20recruitment%20drive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700571851000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F13048%2Fproduction%2F_131769877_gettyimages-516673556_afp976.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67476484%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%2037%20people%20have%20died%20in%20a%20crush%20during%20an%20army%20recruitment%20drive%2C%20Brazzaville%20officials%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A54%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67476484%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67476484.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67476484.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stop%20Misleading%20Advertisements%20or%20Face%20Rs%201%20Crore%20Cost%20for%20False%20Cure%20Claims%3A%20SC%20to%20Patanjali%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21180459%2Framdev.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20November%2021%2C%20asked%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20to%20immediately%20stop%20publishing%20misleading%20claims%20and%20advertisements%20against%20modern%20systems%20of%20medicine%2C%20warning%20of%20a%20hefty%20fine%20if%20it%20does%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-patanjali-baba-ramdev-misleading-advertisements-indian-medical-association-242694%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Ahsanuddin%20Amanullah%20and%20Prashant%20Kumar%20Mishra%20was%20considering%C2%A0a%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20against%20misleading%20advertisements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20such%20false%20and%20misleading%20advertisements%20of%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20have%20to%20stop%20immediately.%20The%20court%20will%20take%20any%20such%20infraction%20very%20seriously%2C%20and%20the%20court%20will%20also%20consider%20imposing%20costs%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20on%20every%20product%20regarding%20which%20a%20false%20claim%20is%20made%20that%20it%20can%20%E2%80%98cure%E2%80%99%20a%20particular%20disease%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Amanullah%20orally%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20directed%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20not%20to%20publish%20any%20such%20advertisements%20in%20the%20future%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20casual%20statements%20are%20not%20made%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20the%20issue%20was%20not%20%E2%80%9Callopathy%20vs%20ayurveda%E2%80%9D%20but%20to%20find%20a%20real%20solution%20to%20the%20problem%20of%20misleading%20medical%20advertisements%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20told%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20K.M.%20Nataraj%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Union%20Government%2C%20to%20find%20a%20%E2%80%9Cviable%20solution%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20problem%20and%20come%20up%20with%20suitable%20recommendations%20after%20consultations.%20The%20matter%20will%20be%20considered%20again%20on%20February%205%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20was%20filed%20in%20mid-2022%20after%20Patanjali%20published%20an%20advertisement%20in%20July%20that%20the%20IMA%20said%20sought%20to%20%E2%80%9Cpromote%20traditional%20medicine%20by%20disparaging%20allopathy%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccontinuous%2C%20systematic%2C%20and%20unabated%20spread%20of%20misinformation%E2%80%9D%20regarding%20allopathy.%20Last%20year%2C%20issuing%20notice%2C%20the%20court%20pulled%20up%20Baba%20Ramdev.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20happened%20to%20Baba%20Ramdev%3F%20He%20can%20popularise%20his%20system%2C%20but%20why%20should%20he%20criticise%20other%20systems.%20We%20all%20respect%20him%2C%20he%20popularised%20yoga%20but%20he%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20criticise%20other%20systems.%20What%20is%20the%20guarantee%20that%20his%20system%20will%20work%3F%20He%20cannot%20refuse%20doctor%20system.%20He%20must%20exercise%20restraint%20in%20abusing%20other%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Framdev-allopathy-sc-smear-campaign%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20N.V.%20Ramana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMA%20petition%20says%20even%20though%20the%20Ministry%20of%20AYUSH%20has%20signed%20a%20Memorandum%20of%20Understanding%20(MoU)%20with%20the%20Advertising%20Standards%20Council%20of%20India%20(ASCI)%20for%20monitoring%20misleading%20advertisements%20of%20AYUSH%20drugs%2C%20Patanjali%20has%20continued%20its%20%E2%80%9Cdisregard%20for%20the%20law%2C%20violating%20the%20mandate%20with%20impunity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20case%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20last%20year%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdelhi-hc-baba-ramdev-allopathy-coronil-covid%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20Baba%20Ramdev%20not%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmislead%E2%80%9D%20people%20against%20allopathy%20and%20not%20to%20make%20any%20claims%20beyond%20what%20authorities%20had%20stated%20about%20Patanjali%E2%80%99s%20product%20Coronil.%20The%20court%20took%20exception%20to%20Patanjali%20advertising%20it%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccure%E2%80%9D%20for%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700571606000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21180459%2Framdev.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmisleading-advertisements-fine-false-cure-claims-supreme-court-patanjali%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20directed%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20not%20to%20publish%20any%20such%20advertisements%20in%20the%20future%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20casual%20statements%20are%20not%20made%20to%20the%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmisleading-advertisements-fine-false-cure-claims-supreme-court-patanjali%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20%26quot%3BPlastic%20Rice%26quot%3B%3A%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Experiment%20With%20Fortified%20Rice%20Hard%20to%20Swallow%20for%20India's%20Adivasi%20Residents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21180212%2FAnumeha-Thumb.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EJharkhand%20and%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20rice%20and%20vegetable%20growing%20small%20cultivators%20question%20the%20logic%20of%20the%20top-down%20nutrition%20fix%20for%20residents%20in%20the%20form%20of%20mandatory%20rice%20fortification.%20Rural%20Adivasi%20residents%20of%20Odisha%20and%20Jharkhand%20question%20the%20new%20rice%20being%20distributed%20to%20them%20as%20food%20subsidies%20in%20the%20public%20distribut