https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmelissa-kerr-uk-and-turkish-officials-to-meet-after-womans-death-from-brazilian-butt-lift-in-istanbul-13012900%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Renaming%20and%20Rebranding%3A%20The%20Story%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Policies%20and%20Schemes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21153357%2Fmodi-manmohan.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Congressman%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20complained%20in%20a%20tweet%20once%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20merely%20changed%20the%20names%20of%2023%20Congress%20schemes%2C%20and%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20running%20a%20%E2%80%9Cname-changing%E2%80%9D%20government%20and%20not%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgame-changing%20one%E2%80%9D%2C%20his%20claim%20was%20put%20to%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20found%20that%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fshashi-tharoor-says-bjp-renamed-23-congress-schemes-he-s-right-about-19%2Fstory-Z6NoIznDj8BSzONlG4KuJM.html%5C%22%3Eright%20about%2019%20schemes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20turned%20out%20that%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Dhan%20Yojana%20was%20the%20UPA%E2%80%99s%20Basic%20Savings%20Bank%20Deposit%20Account%3B%20the%20Beti%20Bachao%2C%20Beti%20Padhao%20Yojana%20was%20the%20same%20as%20the%20National%20Girl%20Child%20Day%20programme%3B%20the%20Deen%20Dayal%20Upadhyaya%20Gram%20Jyoti%20Yojana%20was%20the%20Rajiv%20Grameen%20Vidyutikaran%20Yojana%3B%20the%20Atal%20Mission%20for%20Rejuvenation%20and%20Urban%20Transformation%20was%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20National%20Urban%20Renewal%20Mission%20renamed%3B%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20neem-coated%20urea%20was%20the%20same%20as%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20neem-coated%20urea%3B%20the%20Soil%20Health%20Card%20scheme%20was%20the%20National%20Project%20on%20Management%20of%20Soil%20Health%20and%20Fertility%3B%20the%20Atal%20Pension%20Yojana%20was%20the%20Swavalamban%20Yojana%3B%20and%20even%20Mr%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20%E2%80%9CMake%20in%20India%E2%80%9D%20was%20merely%20the%20National%20Manufacturing%20Policy%20(NMP)%20under%20a%20new%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20was%20not%20mere%20renaming%3B%20the%20entire%20policy%20framework%20in%20many%20cases%20was%20also%20a%20copy-paste%20job%2C%20as%20a%20comparison%20of%20the%20department%20for%20promotion%20of%20industry%20and%20internal%20trade%E2%80%99s%20press%20note%20(2011)%20and%20the%20Make%20in%20India%20website%20page%20on%20national%20manufacturing%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UPA%E2%80%99s%20NMP%20scheme%20spoke%20of%20%E2%80%9Cenhancing%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20in%20GDP%20to%2025%25%20within%20a%20decade%20and%20creating%20100%20million%20jobs%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMake%20in%20India%20seeks%20%E2%80%9Can%20increase%20in%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20GDP%20to%2025%25%E2%80%9D%20and%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccreate%20100%20million%20additional%20jobs%20by%202022%20in%20manufacturing%E2%80%9D.%20The%20UPA%E2%80%99s%20NMP%20says%20it%20will%20%E2%80%9Cincrease%20manufacturing%20sector%20growth%20to%2012-14%25%20over%20the%20medium%20term%E2%80%9D.%20Make%20in%20India%20says%20it%20will%20%E2%80%9Cincrease%20in%20manufacturing%20sector%20growth%20to%2012-14%25%20over%20the%20medium%20term%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NMP%20says%20the%20policy%20needs%20%E2%80%9Ccreation%20of%20appropriate%20skill%20sets%20among%20the%20rural%20migrant%20and%20urban%20poor%20to%20make%20growth%20inclusive%E2%80%9D.%20Make%20in%20India%20says%20it%20needs%20%E2%80%9Ccreation%20of%20appropriate%20skill%20sets%20among%20rural%20migrants%20and%20the%20urban%20poor%20for%20inclusive%20growth%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UPA%20NMP%20policy%20says%20it%20will%20%E2%80%9Cincrease%20domestic%20value%20addition%20and%20technological%20depth%20in%20manufacturing%E2%80%9D.%20Make%20in%20India%20says%20it%20will%20%E2%80%9Cincrease%20domestic%20value%20addition%20and%20technological%20depth%E2%80%9D.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Make%20in%20India%20website%20not%20only%20reflected%20the%20Congress%20scheme%20but%20a%20broken%20download%20link%20also%20unsuccessfully%20directed%20readers%20to%20a%202011%20document%20of%20the%20older%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElsewhere%2C%20Digital%20India%20was%20the%20same%20as%20the%20earlier%20National%20eGovernance%20Plan%3B%20Skill%20India%20the%20same%20as%20the%20National%20Skill%20Development%20Programme%3B%20Mission%20Indradhanush%20was%20the%20Universal%20Immunisation%20Programme%3B%20and%20PAHAL%20the%20earlier%20Direct%20Benefits%20Transfer%20for%20LPG.%20BharatNet%20was%20the%20National%20Optic%20Fibre%20Network%20approved%20on%20October%2025%2C%202011%2C%20aiming%20to%20provide%20broadband%20connectivity%20to%20all%20panchayats.%20When%20the%20Rajiv%20Awaas%20Yojana%20was%20renamed%20the%20Sardar%20Patel%20National%20Urban%20Housing%20Mission%2C%20it%20came%20with%20a%20claim%20from%20then%20housing%20and%20urban%20poverty%20alleviation%20minister%20M.%20Venkaiah%20Naidu%20that%20housing%20for%20all%20would%20come%20by%202022.%20A%20parliamentary%20committee%2C%20headed%20by%20BJD%20MP%20Pinaki%20Mishra%2C%20asked%20the%20government%20how%20merely%20changing%20the%20name%20could%20accelerate%20implementation.%20This%20went%20largely%20unreported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20UPA%E2%80%99s%20schemes%20had%20anodyne%20and%20unmemorable%20names%20even%20though%20they%20had%20the%20same%20aims.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20schemes%20have%20catchier%20names%20because%20he%20spends%20so%20much%20effort%20personally%20polishing%20coinage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20friend%20observed%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20schemes%20targeted%20at%20the%20wealthy%20had%20English%20names%20%E2%80%93%20Digital%20India%2C%20Skill%20India%2C%20Start-up%20India%2C%20Make%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20signalling%20aspiration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20schemes%20for%20the%20poor%20were%20in%20Hindi%20%E2%80%93%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%2C%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Abhiyan%2C%20Beti%20Padhao%20Beti%20Bachao%2C%20Jan%20Dhan%2C%20Garib%20Kalyan%2C%20PM%20Kisan%2C%20Mudra%20Yojana%20%E2%80%93%20reflecting%20the%20branding%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20as%20much%20effort%20on%20implementation%20though%3A%20Make%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20target%20was%20shifted%20from%202022%20to%202025%20as%20manufacturing%20collapsed%20in%20India%2C%20and%20instead%20of%20going%20from%2016%25%20in%202014%20to%2025%25%20in%202022%2C%20in%20fact%20dropped%20to%2013%25%20and%20remained%20at%2013%25%20in%202023.%20Make%20in%20India%20has%20a%20nice%20logo%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETharoor%E2%80%99s%20good-natured%20acceptance%20that%20such%20things%20represented%20continuity%20(Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%20did%20not%20say%20a%20thing%20about%20the%20renaming)%20sat%20in%20contrast%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20contempt%20for%20the%20very%20schemes%20they%20appropriated.%20Particular%20hostility%20was%20reserved%20for%20the%20UPA%E2%80%99s%20Unique%20Identity%20scheme%3A%20Aadhaar.%20During%20the%202014%20campaign%2C%20a%20top%20newspaper%20ran%20a%20headline%20on%20March%2012%2C%202014%3A%20%E2%80%9CAadhaar%20a%20%E2%80%98fraud%E2%80%99%2C%20will%20review%20it%20if%20voted%20to%20power%3A%20BJP%E2%80%9D.%20The%20party%20alleged%20that%20Aadhaar%20was%20a%20criminal%20programme%20and%20it%20would%20have%20the%20CBI%20investigate%20it.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20dangerous%20programme%20to%20regularise%20the%20stay%20of%20illegal%20immigrants%20in%20the%20country.%20Is%20Bharat%20Mata%20so%20open%20to%20illegal%20immigrants%3F%20The%20Aadhaar%20is%20also%20in%20contravention%20of%20Supreme%20Court%20directives%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meenakshi%20Lekhi%20said%20in%20Bengaluru%20while%20campaigning%20against%20Congressman%20and%20Aadhaar%20architect%20Nandan%20Nilekani.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20biometric%20data%20of%20people%20enrolled%20has%20been%20stored%20outside%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%20Nilekani%E2%80%99s%20opponent%2C%20Ananth%20Kumar%20(who%20would%20eventually%20win)%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CAadhaar%20is%20the%20biggest%20fraud%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20month%2C%20Ananth%20Kumar%20said%20the%20BJP%20would%20scrap%20Aadhaar.%20Modi%20himself%20weighed%20in%20against%20Aadhaar%2C%20saying%20the%20money%20spent%20on%20it%20was%20wasted%2C%20that%20NREGA%20was%20meant%20to%20line%20the%20pockets%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20that%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%20was%20useless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20the%20BJP%20under%20Modi%20would%20not%20only%20embrace%20Aadhaar%2C%20it%20would%20also%20force%20it%20upon%20all%20Indians%2C%20willing%20or%20unwilling%2C%20as%20the%20NDA%20expanded%20India%E2%80%99s%20social%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20many%20of%20which%20they%20had%20inherited%20and%20renamed%20to%20pretend%20they%20were%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Faakar-patel%5C%22%3EAakar%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700569816000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21153357%2Fmodi-manmohan.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frenaming-rebranding-bjp-policies-schemes-upa%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20UPA%E2%80%99s%20schemes%20had%20anodyne%20and%20unmemorable%20names%20even%20though%20they%20had%20the%20same%20aims.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20schemes%20have%20catchier%20names%20because%20he%20spends%20so%20much%20effort%20personally%20polishing%20coinage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frenaming-rebranding-bjp-policies-schemes-upa%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OneWeb%20gets%20regulatory%2