3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekarigar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20since%20the%20age%20of%2014.%20But%20in%20nearly%2025%20years%2C%20%E2%80%9Cnever%20has%20our%20work%20dried%20up%20so%20much%20as%20it%20has%20today%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMehmood%20is%20one%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20last%20few%20thousand%20hand-based%20artisans%20or%20weavers.%20Popularly%20seen%20as%20both%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20constituency%20and%20a%20city%20of%20religious%20significance%20for%20Hindus%2C%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Varanasi%20has%20also%20been%20a%20site%20of%20syncretism%2C%20the%20abode%20of%20Lord%20Shiva%20as%20well%20as%20home%20to%20the%20ancient%20Buddhist%20site%20of%20Sarnath%20and%20mediaeval-era%20mosques.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20city%20has%20just%20as%20well%20been%20deeply%20marred%20by%20growing%20communalism%2C%20with%20rising%20Hindu%20nationalist%20politics%20across%20the%20country%20and%20the%20medieval-era%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20now%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fgyanvapi-litmus-test-system-failed%5C%22%3Elegal%20dispute%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20has%20taken%20its%20toll%20on%20the%20area%E2%80%99s%20social%20fabric%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21160831%2Funnamed-14.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21160831%2Funnamed-14.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21160831%2Funnamed-14-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21160831%2Funnamed-14-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685717%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVaranasi%E2%80%99s%20Madanpura%20locality%E2%80%99s%20Banarasi%20silk%20weavers%20seated%20with%20their%20handloom%20shuttles%20as%20they%20work%20on%20weaving%20a%20brocade%20sari%20with%20gold%20zari.%20Photo%3A%20Sabah%20Gurmat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmidst%20all%20this%2C%20Varanasi%20remains%20home%20to%20a%20world-renowned%20community%20of%20weavers%20of%20lustrous%20brocades%20%E2%80%93%20popularly%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Banarasi%E2%80%99.%20Most%20historical%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fpageturner%2Fexcerpt%2Fbenares-brocades-wove-hindu-muslim-peace-for-centuries-but-those-old-ways-changed%2F769291%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccounts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20trace%20the%20origin%20of%20Banarasi%20silks%20to%20somewhere%20between%20the%2016th%20and%20early%2017th%20century%2C%20originating%20in%20Gujarat.%20Those%20from%20the%20region%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20pioneered%20this%20art%20of%20weaving%20silks%20using%20the%20interlacing%20technique%20of%20warp%20and%20weft%20(colloquially%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etana-ban%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%E2%80%99).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20famine%20in%201603%2C%20weaving%20communities%20and%20merchants%20migrated%20from%20Gujarat%20to%20the%20north%2C%20with%20many%20settling%20in%20Varanasi%20and%20receiving%20the%20support%20of%20Mughal%20rulers%2C%20who%20helped%20popularise%20these%20brocades.%20Such%20royal%20patronage%20made%20Banarasi%20silks%20synonymous%20with%20luxury%2C%20with%20this%20attire%20being%20sought%20after%20for%20ceremonial%20and%20festive%20occasions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETill%20the%20late%2020th%20century%2C%20the%20weaves%20remained%20a%20staple%20in%20bridal%20and%20ceremonial%20trousseau%20as%20well%20as%20designerwear.%20But%20the%20past%20few%20decades%20since%20the%201980s%20have%20seen%20a%20steady%20shift%20towards%20mechanisation%2C%20with%20machine-operated%20power%20looms%20squeezing%20the%20handloom%20weavers%20out%20of%20business.%20The%20cost-efficient%20machines%20have%20added%20to%20the%20workers%E2%80%99%20woes%20along%20with%20the%20threat%20of%20cheaper%2C%20mass-produced%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fgallery%2F2022%2F4%2F12%2Fphotos-weavers-of-india-famous-banarasi-sari-are-struggling%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efake%20silk%20saris%20and%20synthetic%20Chinese%20yarn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20replacing%20the%20time-tested%20pure%20silk%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ezari%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(threads%20made%20out%20of%20gold%20or%20silver%20wiring%2C%20usually%20embroidered%20into%20Banarasi%20saris).%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20once%2C%20artisans%20like%20Mehmood%20worked%20on%20%E2%80%9Cat%20least%205%20to%206%20Banarasi%20saris%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20month%2C%20he%20now%20finds%20himself%20receiving%20just%202%20or%203%20commissions%20monthly.%20Hailing%20from%20a%20family%20of%20six%20generations%20of%20weavers%2C%20he%20rues%20that%20the%20industry%20has%20no%20future.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20pure%20silk%20Banarasi%20sari%20sells%20for%20Rs%2040%2C000%20in%20the%20market%2C%20weavers%20like%20me%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20chain%20would%20only%20get%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%203%2C000%20out%20of%20this.%20We%E2%80%99re%20barely%20able%20to%20earn%20Rs%2010%2C000%20a%20month%20now%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnobody%20from%20the%20new%20generation%E2%80%9D%20(including%20his%20own%20children)%20wants%20to%20enter%20this%20line%20of%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdoesnt-matter-if-we-sell-vegetarian-food-how-ups-muslim-restaurant-owners-are-losing-livelihood%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Doesn%E2%80%99t%20Matter%20if%20We%20Sell%20Vegetarian%20Food%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Muslim%20Eatery%20Owners%20Are%20Losing%20Livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMehmood%E2%80%99s%20plight%20is%20not%20unique.%20It%20is%20reflected%20across%20the%20Muslim-dominated%20industry%20of%20weavers%20and%20artisans.%20Although%20there%20are%20no%20recent%20official%20estimates%2C%20Union%20Textile%20Ministry%20data%20from%202019%20says%20that%20the%20city%20is%20home%20to%20at%20least%201%20lakh%20weavers%2C%20and%20houses%20close%20to%2080%2C000%20handlooms.%20Locals%20estimate%20the%20total%20weaving%20population%2C%20including%20artisans%20and%20master%20weavers%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egaddidaars%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0to%20be%20close%20to%203%20lakh.%20But%20these%20numbers%20are%20gradually%20dwindling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20national%20award-winning%20gaddidaar%C2%A0Haseen%20Mohammad%2C%20the%20decline%20began%20in%20the%201990s.%20The%20fourth%20generation%20in%20a%20family%20of%20weavers-turned-intermediary%20producers%2C%20Mohammad%20has%20nearly%2070%20karigars%20working%20under%20him%20in%20the%20older%20part%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20Peeli%20Kothi%20neighbourhood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTill%20the%2090s%2C%20weavers%20who%20used%20their%20hands%20made%20up%2075%25%20of%20the%20silk-weavers%2C%20and%2025%25%20used%20powerloom%20machines.%20Today%2C%20the%20situation%20is%20the%20opposite%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20barely%2025%25%20of%20the%20industry%20has%20handloom%20weavers%20now.%20He%20estimates%20that%20close%20to%201.5%20lakh%20weavers%20in%20the%20city%20work%20in%20power%20looms%20and%20only%2025%2C000%20are%20left%20working%20by%20hand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20influx%20of%20power%20loom%20machines%20has%20not%20only%20sounded%20the%20death%20knell%20for%20weavers%20using%20the%20ancient%20handloom%20technique%2C%20but%20the%20shift%20to%20modernisation%20has%20also%20come%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20quality.%20The%20market%20for%20Banarasi%20silks%20has%20been%20flooded%20by%20cheaper%20polyester%20and%20Chinese%20silk%20yarns%2C%20fake%20zari%2C%20and%20machine-made%20weaves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpreading%20out%20an%20intricately%20woven%20tanchoi%20silk%20sari%2C%20Mohammad%20emphasises%2C%20%E2%80%9CHandloom%20karigars%20make%20real%20silk%20saris%2C%20but%20the%20market%20is%20full%20of%20fakes%20thanks%20to%20power%20loom%20machines.%20Most%20people%20cannot%20tell%20the%20products%20apart%2C%20but%2090-95%25%20of%20powerloom%20saris%20use%20fake%2C%20cheap%20materials.%20Where%20we%20need%2010%20days%20to%20make%20one%20sari%20by%20hand%2C%20they%20can%20make%203-4%20saris%20in%20just%20one%20day%20using%20the%20machine%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20those%20such%20as%2054-year-old%20weaver%20Mohammad%20Ahmad%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20power%20loom%20machines%20is%20%E2%80%9Ca%20byproduct%20of%20the%201990s%20and%20the%20Narasimha%20Rao%20government%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said%20while%20pointing%20out%20that%20liberalisation%20and%20privatisation%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20their%20decline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAhmad%20informed%20this%20reporter%20that%20he%20and%20four%20of%20his%20brothers%20have%20been%20doing%20this%20work%20for%20over%20five%20generations.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20us%2C%20even%20four%20of%20my%20own%20children%2C%20are%20associated%20with%20weaving.%20But%20it%20is%20very%20bad%20for%20us%20right%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20rued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21161010%2Funnamed-1-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21161010%2Funnamed-1-2.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21161010%2Funnamed-1-2-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21161010%2Funnamed-1-2-768x1024.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685718%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Ahmad%20from%20Nati%20Imli%20weavers%E2%80%99%20colony%20demonstrates%20the%20use%20of%20a%20power%20loom%20machine.%20He%20estimates%20that%20the%20original%20handloom%20Banarasi%20silk%20weavers%20now%20make%20up%20less%20than%2020-25%25%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20weavers.%20Photo%3A%20Sabah%20Gurmat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20a%20lack%20of%20institutional%20support%20and%20existing%20policies%20leaves%20weavers%20in%20the%20lurch%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20no%20recent%20official%20data%20exists%2C%20locals%20and%20academic%20experts%20both%20assert%20that%20Muslims%20make%20up%20a%20majority%20of%20Varanasi%E2%80%99s%20skilled%20Banarasi%20silk%20artisans%2C%20with%20many%20estimating%20between%2070%20to%2080%25%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20weaving%20community%20to%20be%20Muslims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202007%2C%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhandlooms.nic.in%2Fassets%2Fimg%2FPublications%2FBanaras%2520Brocades%2520and%2520Sarees635701527534407243.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%20published%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20Textiles%20Committee%2C%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20textile%20ministry%2C%20said%20that%20the%20master%20weavers%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egrihasts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0are%20mostly%20Muslims%2C%20and%20the%20weavers%20or%20karigars%20working%20under%20them%20are%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%20The%20report%20also%20notes%20that%20%E2%80%9Cabout%2070%25%20of%20the%20weaving%20force%20belongs%20to%20Banaras%20city%E2%80%A6of%20which%2C%2090%25%20are%20Muslims.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20prominent%20weavers%E2%80%99%20community%20leader%2C%20Sardar%20Maqbool%20Hassan%2C%20concurs.%20Speaking%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Hassan%20said%20that%20Varanasi%20has%20at%20least%202%20lakh%20power%20looms%2C%20%E2%80%9Cand%20Muslims%20would%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20constitute%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20least%2070%25%20of%20the%20labour%20in%20these.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHassan%20believes%20that%20the%20large%20industrial%20presence%20of%20Muslim%20weavers%20gives%20a%20feeling%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbeing%20indirectly%20targeted%E2%80%9D.%20Enlisting%20the%20gaps%20in%20schemes%20and%20policies%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEver%20since%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20has%20come%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20schemes%20meant%20for%20weavers%20have%20been%20shut%20down%2C%20such%20as%20the%20weavers%E2%80%99%20ID%20cards%20which%20allowed%20us%20to%20access%20Bahudi%20funds.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bahudi%20fund%20scheme%20helped%20weavers%20access%20credit%20for%20covering%20medical%20costs%2C%20expenses%20for%20healthcare%20and%2C%20as%20per%20Hassan%2C%20%E2%80%9Calso%20assisted%20in%20getting%20our%20daughters%20married%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhomes-demolished-the-right-to-fish-denied-the-lives-of-gujarats-muslim-fishermen%5C%22%3EHomes%20Demolished%2C%20the%20Right%20to%20Fish%20Denied%3A%20The%20Lives%20of%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Muslim%20Fishermen%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%20for%20Umm-e-Habiba%2C%20the%20twin%20policies%20of%20demonetisation%20and%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Goods%20%26amp%3B%20Services%20Tax%20or%20%E2%80%98GST%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20which%20came%20into%20effect%20under%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%202016%20and%202017%20respectively%20%E2%80%93%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Felections%2Fvaranasi-weavers-handlooms-woes-post-noteban-and-gst-not-a-poll-issue-narendra-modi-shalini-yadav-5718714%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emade%20life%20difficult%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Women%20weavers%20such%20as%20Habiba%20make%20up%20nearly%2020%20to%2022%25%20of%20the%20overall%20weaving%20community%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHabiba%20works%20in%20a%20warehouse%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Mubarakpur%20located%20nearly%2096%20kilometres%20from%20Varanasi.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20GST%20of%2012%25%20on%20our%20work%20and%20a%205%25%20tax%20on%20yarn.%20If%20a%20Banarasi%20silk%20sari%20is%20sold%20for%20Rs%2010%2C000%2C%20handloom%20weavers%20like%20me%20will%20earn%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%202%2C000%2C%20but%20now%20with%20GST%20and%20demonetisation%2C%20even%20that%20earning%20has%20dropped%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%2024-year%20old%20added%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20advent%20of%20power%20loom%20machines%20has%20also%20pushed%20women%20out%20of%20the%20industry.%20Until%20a%20few%20decades%20ago%2C%20women%20%E2%80%93%20usually%20daughters%2C%20wives%20and%20others%20from%20weaving%20households%20%E2%80%93%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20cutting%20of%20threads%20and%20rolling%20of%20yarn%2C%20but%20this%20work%20has%20now%20been%20mechanised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21161232%2Funnamed-2-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21161232%2Funnamed-2-2.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21161232%2Funnamed-2-2-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21161232%2Funnamed-2-2-768x1024.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685720%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E24-year-old%20Umm-e-Habiba%2C%20who%20weaves%20on%20a%20handloom%20shuttle%2C%20works%20on%20a%20kattan%20silk%20yarn%20in%20Mubarakpur%20town.%20Photo%3A%20Sabah%20Gurmat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20not%20everyone%20agrees%20with%20locally%20popular%20perceptions%20regarding%20the%20weavers%E2%80%99%20decline.%20Shahid%20Junaid%2C%20an%20industry%20insider%20and%20master-weaver%20from%20the%20reputed%20house%20of%20Haji%20Munna%20weavers%2C%C2%A0%20feels%20that%20%E2%80%9Cseveral%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20schemes%20have%20been%20well-intentioned%E2%80%9D%2C%20conceding%20that%20their%20implementation%20was%20a%20bigger%20problem%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJunaid%20enlisted%20a%20number%20of%20schemes%20under%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20government%20that%20were%20launched%20with%20much%20fanfare%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Cno%20one%20knows%20now%20what%20has%20become%20of%20them%E2%80%9D.%20An%20eighth-generation%20weaver%2C%20Junaid%20points%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Usttad%20Yojana%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98One%20District%20One%20Product%20(ODOP)%E2%80%99%20and%20other%20initiatives%20in%20this%20regard%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202015%2C%20then%20union%20and%20minority%20affairs%20minister%20Mukhtar%20Abbas%20Naqvi%20launched%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2Fnewsite%2FPrintRelease.aspx%3Frelid%3D121767%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98USTTAD%E2%80%99%20scheme%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20aimed%20at%20%E2%80%9Censuring%20the%20growth%20of%20traditional%20artisans%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20city.%20At%20the%20launch%2C%20Naqvi%20had%20also%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20provide%20jobs%20to%20youths%20from%20the%20minority%20community.%20But%20Junaid%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20go%20and%20ask%20every%20weaver%2C%20but%20nobody%20here%20would%20know%20how%20to%20avail%20this%20scheme%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UP%20government%E2%80%99s%20similarly%20hyped%20One%20District%20One%20Product%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthefederal.com%2Fstates%2Fnorth%2Futtar-pradesh%2Fups-odop-scheme-one-district-one-product-3-sets-of-export-data%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EODOP)%20initiative%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20aimed%20at%20promoting%20manufacturing%20growth%20in%20the%20state%2C%20invoked%20a%20similar%20response.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ODOP%20scheme%20promises%20loans%2C%20but%20our%20community%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20loans%20with%20high-interest%20rates%20that%20make%20it%20far%20too%20inaccessible.%20How%20will%20an%20unlettered%20population%20of%20karigars%20be%20filing%20papers%20and%20keep%20going%20to%20offices%3F%20Weavers%20need%20and%20want%20the%20government%20to%20buy%20our%20products%2C%20like%20they%20used%20to%20with%20Cottage%20Emporium%2C%20All%20India%20Handloom%20Fabrics%20Marketing%20Co-operative%20and%20others%E2%80%9D%2C%20Junaid%20emphasised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaster%20weaver%20Haseen%20Mohammad%20agrees.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20put%20this%2C%20but%20since%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20Yogi%20government%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20expect%20the%20government%20to%20provide%20patronage%20to%20cottage%20industries%20like%20ours.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fin-indias-brass-city-an-overwhelmingly-muslim-workforce-stares-at-a-looming-crisis%5C%22%3EIn%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Brass%20City%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20Overwhelmingly%20Muslim%20Workforce%20Stares%20at%20a%20Looming%20Crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EElectricity%20subsidies%20have%20also%20proven%20to%20be%20an%20issue%20of%20contention%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20helmed%20by%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20which%20in%202019%20did%20away%20with%20the%20flat%20rate%20subsidy%20measure%20for%20power%20loom%20weavers.%20The%20subsidy%20scheme%20was%20first%20introduced%20by%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%E2%80%99s%20(SP)%20government%20in%20the%20year%202006%2C%20and%20following%20the%20BJP-led%20government%E2%80%99s%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20scheme%20in%202019%2C%20it%20was%20reinstated%20in%20April%202023%20after%20much%20protest.%20Now%20known%20as%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20Power%20Loom%20Weaver%20Electricity%20Flat%20Rate%20Scheme%2C%20the%20intervention%20has%20drawn%20flak%20again%2C%20thanks%20to%20weavers%20having%20to%20shell%20out%20much%20higher%20bills%20under%20the%20new%20scheme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECommunity%20leader%20Sardar%20Maqbool%20Hassan%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20handloom%20usage%20declined%20drastically%2C%20the%20subsidies%20for%20electricity%20came%20to%20be%20in%202006%20which%20mainly%20benefited%20powerlooms.%20When%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%202017%2C%20things%20changed.%20Till%20SP%E2%80%99s%20time%2C%20we%20paid%20Rs%2075%20as%20electricity%20bill%20each%20month%2C%20per%20loom.%20After%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%2C%20they%20instituted%20a%20policy%20which%20said%20that%20up%20to%20120%20units%20of%20electricity%20per%20powerloom%20would%20receive%20subsidies%20but%20after%20that%2C%20you%20would%20be%20charged.%20This%20year%2C%20we%20ended%20up%20paying%20Rs%20400%20instead%20of%20Rs%2075.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHassan%20argued%20that%20as%20per%20the%20new%20scheme%2C%20weavers%20using%20up%20to%20five%20kilowatts%20(kW)%20of%20electricity%20were%20paying%20bills%20that%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Flucknow-news%2Fvaranasi-powerloom-weavers-oppose-relaunched-flat-rate-electricity-scheme-demand-rollback-of-new-norms-101684520624269.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DLikewise%252C%2520rural%2520weavers%2520with%2520connection%2Ceach%2520connection%252C%25E2%2580%259D%2520he%2520added.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cover%20five%20times%20higher%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20than%20the%20previous%20rates%20even%20after%20accounting%20for%20natural%20price%20rises.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOthers%2C%20such%20as%20weaver%20Mohammad%20Ahmad%20claim%20that%20the%20political%20tussle%20over%20subsidies%20goes%20deeper.%20Ahmad%20appears%20wary%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Creligious%20divide%E2%80%9D%2C%20stressing%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98Bunkar%20(weaver)%20Hindu%20Yuva%20Vahini%E2%80%99%20helmed%20by%20one%20Shailendra%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20big%20gaddidaars%20and%20master-weavers%20with%20at%20least%2020-30%20looms%20each%2C%20and%20have%20more%20resources.%20They%20even%20took%20out%20a%20bike%20rally%2C%20and%20are%20lobbying%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20state%20authorities%20to%20receive%20subsidies%20even%20when%20they%20are%20not%20small-time%20weavers%20who%20need%20it.%20They%20want%20a%20subsidy%20up%20to%2025kW%2C%20whereas%20the%20present%20subsidy%20is%20only%20until%205kW%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20contacted%2C%20however%2C%20Singh%20denied%20these%20claims.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20formed%20an%20organisation%20trying%20to%20collectivise%20weavers%20across%20religious%20and%20caste%20lines%2C%20because%20weavers%20here%20have%20no%20unions.%20It%20is%20called%20the%20Varanasi%20Vastra%20Bunkar%20Sangathan%2C%20and%20over%203000%20weavers%20have%20joined%20us%20so%20far.%20One%20of%20the%20co-founders%2C%20Aslam%20Ansari%20is%20also%20a%20Muslim%20from%20a%20master%20weaver%E2%80%99s%20family%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21161408%2Funnamed-3-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21161408%2Funnamed-3-2.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21161408%2Funnamed-3-2-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21161408%2Funnamed-3-2-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685722%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHaji%20Munna%20Creations%E2%80%99%20Shahid%20Junaid%2C%20the%20eighth%20generation%20in%20a%20family%20of%20master-weavers%2C%20sits%20next%20to%20a%20pile%20of%20pure%20silk%20brocades%20ready%20to%20be%20shipped%20to%20outside%20buyers.%20Photo%3A%20Sabah%20Gurmat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELocal%20weavers%20caught%20amidst%20growing%20social%20and%20religious%20fissures%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20weavers%20such%20as%20Ahmad%20and%20Maqbool%20Hassan%20caution%20against%20the%20growing%20religious%20divide%20amongst%20weavers%2C%20adding%20to%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20woes%20is%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20famous%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20which%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20key%20site%20of%20legal%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fvaranasi-gyanvapi-mosque-kashi-vishwanath-temple-complex-dispute-explained-8146388%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edispute%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20far-right%20consolidation%20amongst%20local%20Hindus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20hearings%20ongoing%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%2C%20many%20believe%20the%20issue%20has%20galvanised%20weavers%20along%20communal%20lines.%20Abbas%20Ali%2C%20a%20weaver%20in%20the%20Bajardiha%20neighbourhood%2C%20said%20that%20while%20the%20production%20side%20had%20historically%20seen%20mostly%20Muslims%20involved%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20traders%20and%20sellers%20of%20raw%20materials%20like%20zari%20have%20mostly%20been%20Hindus.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20sense%20that%20more%20of%20them%20do%20not%20want%20to%20supply%20or%20buy%20from%20us%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Singh%20believes%20that%20no%20such%20friction%20exists%20now.%20%E2%80%9CWeaving%20has%20become%20more%20equitably%20divided.%20When%20more%20handloom%20work%20existed%2C%2095%25%20of%20the%20weavers%20were%20Muslim.%20But%20power%20looms%20have%20changed%20this%20equation%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20now%20a%2060%20to%2040%20ratio%20of%20Muslims%20and%20Hindus%20in%20the%20Banarasi%20silk%20industry%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBetween%20contesting%20claims%2C%20though%2C%20locals%20also%20point%20to%20the%20growing%20dissatisfaction%20causing%20many%20to%20migrate%20away%20from%20producing%20the%20heritage%20silks.%20The%20absence%20of%20opportunities%20and%20documented%20fall%20in%20handloom%20work%20has%20pushed%20many%20to%20move%20to%20greener%20pastures%2C%20with%20textile%20hubs%20such%20as%20Surat%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20Ludhiana%20emerging%20as%20top%20draws.%20Here%20too%2C%20some%20point%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Cquiet%20moving%20away%20of%20Muslims%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20K%2C%20a%20prominent%20gaddidaar%20who%20claimed%20to%20supply%20to%20premium%20labels%20such%20as%20Raw%20Mango%2C%20Taniera%20and%20the%20Aditya%20Birla%20Group%20among%20others%2C%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20future%20in%20the%20trade.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20from%20our%20community%20(Muslims)%C2%A0%20have%20migrated%20and%20left%20Banaras.%20There%20is%20a%20massive%20migration%20away%20from%20Varanasi%20and%20I%20feel%20this%20has%20amplified%20since%20the%202010s.%20People%20are%20going%20to%20work%20in%20bigger%20cities%20like%20Surat%20and%20Bengaluru%2C%20because%20there%20is%20more%20money%20out%20there.%20No%20one%20sees%20a%20lucrative%20future%20here%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fwide-range-of-fears-new-indias-muslims-have%5C%22%3EHow%20Are%20India%E2%80%99s%20Muslims%20Feeling%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHassan%20further%20enunciates%20this%2C%20citing%20economic%20prospects.%20%E2%80%9CA%20weaver%20here%2C%20on%20a%20good%20day%20can%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%20300%20whereas%20in%20Bengaluru%20they%E2%80%99d%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%20600.%20Why%20would%20I%20want%20to%20keep%20living%20here%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHassan%20believes%20the%20only%20way%20out%20is%20to%20incentivise%20weavers%2C%20and%20the%20government%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20weaving%20community.%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20that%20they%20consider%20the%20profession%20to%20be%20an%20all-Muslim%20one.%20In%20reality%2C%20Muslims%20along%20with%20others%20(Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%20and%20several%20backward%20castes%20across%20groups)%20are%20all%20weavers%2C%20all%20of%20us%20will%20suffer%20and%20all%20of%20us%20benefit%20if%20they%20truly%20wish%20to%20uplift%20us%20and%20our%20craft.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ESabah%20Gurmat%20is%20an%20independent%20journalist%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20This%20story%20is%20part%20of%20an%20ongoing%20series%20on%20the%20socio-economic%20decline%20of%20industries%20and%20businesses%20led%20by%20Muslims.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EReporting%20for%20her%20article%20was%20supported%20by%20the%20International%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Media%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20Howard%20G.%20Buffett%20Fund%20for%20Women%20Journalists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700566526000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21161408%2Funnamed-3-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fvaranasi-muslim-silk-weavers-mechanisation-communalism%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20absence%20of%20opportunities%20and%20a%20documented%20fall%20in%20handloom%20work%20has%20pushed%20many%20to%20move%20to%20other%20textile%20hubs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fvaranasi-muslim-silk-weavers-mechanisation-communalism%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Private%20equity%2C%20venture%20capital%20investments%20dropped%20to%20%243.4%20bn%20in%20October%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700566022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-05%2F26%2Ffull%2F1685103974-5133.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fstock-market-news%2Fprivate-equity-venture-capital-investments-drop-to-3-4-bn-in-oct-report-123112100688_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20value%2C%20the%20bets%20were%203%20per%20cent%20lower%20than%20the%20%243.5%20billion%20in%20the%20year-ago%20period%2C%20and%2019%20per%20cent%20lower%20than%20the%20%244.2%20billion%20in%20September%2C%20shows%20IVCA-EY%20report%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engage