s.com.%2Farticle%2Findia%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-rescue-plans-9035674%2F%5C%22%3Eauthorities%20devised%20a%20five-pronged%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20rescue%20the%20workers%2C%20which%20involves%20drilling%20vertically%20from%20the%20top%20of%20the%20hill%20the%20tunnel%20goes%20through%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%E2%80%98micro-drilling%E2%80%99%20through%20the%20tunnel%E2%80%99s%20left%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHorizontal%20drilling%20from%20the%20tunnel%E2%80%99s%20Barkot%20end%20has%20also%20commenced%2C%20the%20roads%20ministry%20said%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvisory%20to%20TV%20channels%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20issued%20an%20advisory%20to%20TV%20channels%20that%20are%20covering%20the%20rescue%20mission%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20telecast%20of%20video%20footage%20and%20other%20pictures%20by%20placing%20cameras%20and%20other%20equipment%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20the%20site%20%E2%80%9Chave%20the%20potential%20to%20adversely%20affect%20the%20ongoing%3Cbr%3E%5Cnoperations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20asked%20the%20channels%20to%20refrain%20from%20sensationalising%20the%20issue%20and%20broadcasting%20any%20live%20videos%20from%20close%20proximity%20of%20the%20tunnel%20site.%20It%20said%20the%20media%20should%20ensure%20that%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20various%20agencies%20are%20in%20no%20way%20disrupted%20or%20disturbed%20by%20the%20very%20presence%20of%20cameramen%2C%20reporters%20or%20equipment%20near%20or%20around%20the%20operations%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20also%20advised%20to%20be%20cautious%20and%20sensitive%20while%20reporting%20on%20the%20matter%20especially%20in%20putting%20out%20headlines%2C%20videos%20%26amp%3B%20images%20and%20take%20due%20care%20of%20the%20sensitive%20nature%20of%20operation%2C%20psychological%20status%20of%20the%20family%20members%20and%20as%20well%20as%20the%20viewers%20in%20general%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20advisory%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EForeign%20experts%20drafted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20experts%20have%20been%20drafted%20in%20for%20the%20rescue%20operation%2C%20including%20independent%20disaster%20investigator%20Arnold%20Dix%2C%20who%20is%20president%20of%20the%20International%20Tunneling%20and%20Underground%20Space%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Uttarkashi%20(Uttarakhand)%20tunnel%20rescue%20operation%20%7C%20International%20Tunneling%20Expert%2C%20Arnold%20Dix%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20fantastic%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20news%20we%20have%20had%20over%20the%20last%20few%20hours.%20It%20is%20great%20to%20see%20the%20faces%20of%20those%20men%20that%20we%20are%20going%20to%20bring%20home.%20We%20have%20food%20going%20to%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Ft5f47dPgbu%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Ft5f47dPgbu%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1726825095241531762%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2021%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20a%20900-millimetre%20wide%20pipe%20that%20rescuers%20plan%20to%20use%20to%20retrieve%20the%20trapped%20workers%2C%20Dix%20told%20ANI%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cby%20far%20the%20best%20and%20fastest%20means%20to%20get%20the%20men%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20has%20its%20technical%20difficulties%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%E2%80%99re%20doing%20multiple%20rescue%20missions%20%E2%80%93%20we%E2%80%99ve%20got%20missions%20from%20the%20top%2C%20missions%20from%20the%20front%2C%20%5Ba%5D%20mission%20from%20the%20side.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ANI%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faninews.in%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgeneral-news%2Fsilkyara-tunnel-collapse-brief-setback-to-rescue-operations-as-narrow-road-prevents-piling-machine-movement20231121114643%2F%5C%22%3Erescue%20work%20was%20delayed%20on%20Tuesday%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20a%20piling%20machine%20being%20transported%20to%20the%20tunnel%20became%20stuck%20due%20to%20the%20road%20it%20was%20travelling%20on%20being%20too%20narrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Fwere-in-bad-condition-please-get-us-out-fast-trapped-mens-desperate-cry%2Farticleshow%2F105365999.cms%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20one%20of%20the%20trapped%20workers%20as%20telling%20a%20government%20official%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20are%20getting%20food%2C%20but%20all%20of%20us%20are%20in%20bad%20condition%20%E2%80%A6%20it%20is%20getting%20harder%20and%20harder%20with%20each%20passing%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20said%20that%20at%20least%20three%20of%20the%20workers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67471018%5C%22%3Ereported%20having%20dysentery%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20authorities%20were%20providing%20them%20with%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20were%20working%20on%20part%20of%20a%20new%20national%20highway%2C%20the%20Char%20Dham%20all-weather%20road%2C%20a%20flagship%20federal%20project%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20that%20aims%20to%20reduce%20travel%20times%20between%20four%20ancient%20Hindu%20pilgrimage%20sites%20in%20Uttarakhand%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20also%20improve%20access%20to%20strategic%20areas%20of%20the%20country%20near%20the%20border%20with%20regional%20rival%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findia-rescuers-plan-new-escape-route-for-41-trapped-workers%2Fa-67486291%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700559942000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21144558%2FTunnel-vision.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Futtarkashi-camera-first-visuals-of-trapped-tunnel-workers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20six-inch%20pipe%20through%20which%20a%20medical%20camera%20reached%20the%2041%20trapped%20workers%20was%20reportedly%20also%20prepared%20yesterday%20to%20get%20them%20their%20first%20hot%20meal%20since%20the%20collapse%20on%20November%2012.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Futtarkashi-camera-first-visuals-of-trapped-tunnel-workers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Logic%20and%20Compassion%20Behind%20the%20Rajasthan%20Government's%20Many%20Schemes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21144259%2F24083848365_f5f794c540_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot-led%20government%20in%20Rajasthan%20has%20passed%20a%20slew%20of%20progressive%20welfare%20policies.%20With%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20due%20later%20this%20month%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20accused%20the%20state%20government%20of%20using%20welfare%20policies%20merely%20as%20a%20means%20to%20remain%20in%20power.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20some%20economists%2C%20particularly%20those%20working%20with%20the%20NDA%20government%20at%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20have%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20need%20and%20importance%20of%20such%20policies.%20However%2C%20such%20concerns%20appear%20to%20be%20misplaced.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20355px)%2085vw%2C%20355px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22355%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22293%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20July%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20passed%20the%20Minimum%20Guaranteed%20Income%20Act%20(MGIA)%2C%20which%20guarantees%20all%20families%20in%20rural%20and%20urban%20areas%20125%20days%20of%20work%20in%20a%20year.%20The%20act%20combines%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(a%20central%20government%20Act)%20with%20a%20State%20Act%2C%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Urban%20Employment%20Scheme%20(IGUES)%2C%20launched%20last%20year.%20While%20MGNREGA%20targets%20rural%20households%2C%20IGUES%20is%20for%20urban%20residents.%20With%20the%20IGUES%2C%20Rajasthan%20became%20only%20the%20sixth%20state%20in%20the%20country%20to%20have%20an%20urban%20employment%20guarantee%20scheme.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20what%20differentiates%20Rajasthan%20is%20that%20the%20scheme%20is%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20unlike%20other%20states.%20Economists%2C%20for%20long%2C%20have%20been%20urging%20the%20central%20government%20for%20the%20same%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcse.azimpremjiuniversity.edu.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FSWI2019_Urban_Job_Guarantee.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eecological%20degradation%2C%20mediocre%20infrastructure%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20relatively%20thinner%20social%20safety%20net%2C%20high%20unemployment%20rates%2C%20and%20poor%20quality%20low%20wage%20jobs%20in%20urban%20areas%20make%20it%20a%20necessity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMGIA%20also%20guarantees%20a%20pension%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%20the%20elderly%2C%20disabled%2C%20widows%2C%20and%20divorced%20women%2C%20which%20will%20be%20increased%20by%2015%25%20every%20year.%20This%20amount%20is%20double%20the%20previous%20pension%20amount%20of%20Rs%20500%20and%20covers%20almost%201%20crore%20beneficiaries%2C%20i.e.%2C%20nearly%20one%20in%20every%20eight%20people%20in%20the%20state.%20This%20increase%20takes%20the%20state%20share%20of%20pension%20expenditure%20in%20Rajasthan%20to%2097%25%2C%20with%20the%20central%20government%20contributing%20Rs%20367%20crores%20for%20its%20measly%20Rs%20200%20national%20pension%20%E2%80%93%20an%20amount%20that%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20increased%20since%202006%20despite%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Fpolicy%2Fahead-of-budget-economists-demand-increase-in-social-security-pension-and-maternity-benefits%2Farticleshow%2F96003228.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erepeated%20advice%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20economists%20and%20other%20experts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EElsewhere%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20launched%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20Folk%20Artist%20Promotion%20Scheme%20on%2011th%20August%2C%20which%20guarantees%20100%20days%20of%20employment%20at%20government%20events%20to%20all%20folk%20artists%20in%20the%20state%20and%20a%20one-time%20transfer%20of%20Rs%205%2C000%20to%20buy%20music%20equipment.%20This%20initiative%20will%20work%20wonders%20in%20preserving%20or%20even%20reviving%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Fmagazine%2F1039664%2Fthe-world-of-rajasthani-folk-music-is-shrinking-despite-its-fame-and-success%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshrinking%20world%20of%20Rajasthani%20folk%20art%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20uplifting%20historically%20neglected%20nomadic%20tribes%20like%20Kalbeliyas%2C%20Langas%2C%20and%20Manganiyars%2C%20which%20form%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20folk%20artists%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20estimates%20based%20on%20NSSO%20surveys%20by%20Brookings%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F201612_health-and-morbidity.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enearly%207%25%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20population%20is%20pushed%20into%20poverty%20every%20year%20due%20to%20unbearable%20healthcare%20costs.%20The%20Infant%20Mortality%20Rate%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20Sample%20Registration%20System%20data%2C%20is%2032%20per%20thousand%20live%20births%2C%20whereas%20the%20Maternal%20Mortality%20Rate%20stands%20at%20113%20per%20100%2C000%20live%20births%20%E2%80%93%20both%20significantly%20higher%20than%20the%20national%20average.%20Alarmingly%2C%20anaemia%20also%20witnessed%20a%C2%A0%20rise%20in%20Rajasthan%20between%20the%204th%20(2015-16)%20and%20the%205th%20(2019-20)%20rounds%20of%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey.%20For%20children%20up%20to%20five%20years%20of%20age%2C%20anaemia%20rose%20from%2060.3%25%20to%2071.5%25.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoreover%2C%20according%20to%20NITI%20Aayog%E2%80%99s%20latest%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fsocial.niti.gov.in%2Fhlt-ranking%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehealth%20index%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20is%20a%20composite%20score%20of%20overall%20health%20performance%20based%20on%2024%20indicators%2C%20Rajasthan%20ranked%2016th%20among%2019%20large%20states.%20In%20this%20light%2C%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Right%20to%20Health%20Care%20Act%2C%20passed%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20which%20guarantees%20free%20emergency%20treatment%20to%20everyone%2C%20is%20historic.%20However%2C%20it%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20bill%E2%80%99s%20final%20version%20was%20diluted%20by%20weakening%20grievance%20redressal%20mechanisms%20and%20eliminating%20civil%20society%20participation%20in%20the%20oversight%20committee%20due%20to%20incessant%20lobbying%20by%20primarily%20private%20doctor%20bodies.%20Over%2090%25%20of%20private%20hospitals%20in%20the%20state%20will%20now%20not%20be%20under%20the%20bill%E2%80%99s%20ambit%2C%20leaving%20only%2047%20private%20hospitals%20across%20the%20state%20eligible%20for%20the%20Act.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20government%20also%20increased%20its%20universal%20insurance%20coverage%20under%20Chiranjeevi%20Scheme%20from%20Rs%2010%20lakhs%20to%20Rs%2025%20lakhs.%20Since%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20inception%20in%202021%2C%20over%201.35%20crore%20families%20have%20enrolled%2C%20and%20more%20than%2015%20lakh%20people%20have%20already%20availed%20of%20its%20benefits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F04172617%2FMGNREGA-copy.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20building%20a%20pond%20as%20part%20of%20MGNREGA%20work.%20Credit%3A%20UN%20Women%2FGaganjit%20Singh%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-188629%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWomen%20building%20a%20pond%20as%20part%20of%20MGNREGA%20work.%20Representational%20image.%20Photo%3A%20UN%20Women%2FGaganjit%20Singh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Gehlot%20government%20also%20passed%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20gas%20subsidy%20scheme%2C%20which%20provides%20LPG%20cylinders%20to%20over%2076%20Lakh%20poorest%20households%20at%20a%20flat%20rate%20of%20Rs%20500%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20subsidy%20of%20Rs%20450%20at%20current%20prices.%20To%20understand%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20importance%2C%20consider%20this%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fnews%2Fenergy%2Fujjwala-over-9-million-beneficiaries-did-not-refill-cylinder-last-year-centre-admits-84130%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%202021-22%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20out%20of%20about%209.6%20crore%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Ujjawala%20Yojana%20(PMUY)%20beneficiaries%2C%2010%25%20took%20no%20refill%2C%2011%25%20took%20only%20one%20while%2057%25%20took%204%20or%20fewer%20refills%20according%20to%20government%20data%20whereas%20non-PMUY%20consumers%20refilled%20their%20cylinders%207%20times%20on%20average%20in%20the%20year.%20The%20reason%20behind%20this%20is%20the%20skyrocketing%20price%20of%20LPG%2C%20which%20went%20from%20Rs%20574%20in%20August%202019%20to%20Rs%20949%20in%20March%E2%80%9922%20in%20Delhi.%20Furthermore%2C%20prices%20of%20necessities%20such%20as%20pulses%2C%20oils%2C%20sugar%2C%20and%20spices%20have%20also%20increased%20rapidly%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20Hence%2C%20the%20Annapurna%20scheme%2C%20launched%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20which%20provides%20one%20kg%20of%20dal%2C%20sugar%2C%20salt%2C%20edible%20oil%2C%20and%20spices%20for%20free%20to%20families%20covered%20by%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%20(NFSA)%2C%20was%20a%20major%20relief.%20The%20inclusion%20of%20oils%20and%20pulses%20in%20PDS%20entitlements%20had%20been%20a%20long-standing%20demand%20of%20food%20security%20activists%20and%20economists%20alike%20to%20help%20meet%20the%20nutritional%20needs%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurthermore%2C%20in%202020%2C%20the%20Gehlot%20government%20launched%20Indira%20Rasois%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20person%20has%20to%20sleep%20hungry.%20Indira%20rasois%20are%20community%20kitchens%20that%20provide%20a%20warm%2C%20nutritious%20meal%20at%20just%20%E2%82%B98%20per%20thali.%20To%20date%2C%201000%20urban%20kitchens%20have%20served%20more%20than%2015%20crore%20meals%2C%20according%20to%20the%20government%2C%20with%201000%20additional%20kitchens%20in%20rural%20areas%20opening%20soon%20in%20the%20state.%20With%20the%20gas%20subsidy%2C%20Indira%20Rasois%2C%20and%20the%20Annapurna%20scheme%2C%20Rajasthan%20has%20perhaps%20taken%20the%20boldest%20steps%20in%20the%20country%20to%20reduce%20hunger%20and%20provide%20relief%20from%20inflation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%2024%2C%20Rajasthan%20became%20the%20first%20state%20in%20the%20country%20to%20pass%20a%20social%20security%20act%20for%20its%20over%203%20lakh%20gig%20workers.%20The%20Act%20will%20establish%20a%20welfare%20board%20for%20gig%20workers%20where%20registered%20gig%20workers%20will%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20be%20heard%20for%20grievances%20and%20participate%20in%20decision-making%20in%20addition%20to%20being%20eligible%20for%20general%20and%20specific%20social%20security%20schemes.%20Over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20issues%20such%20as%20long%20working%20hours%2C%20meagre%20pay%2C%20lack%20of%20insurance%20and%20social%20security%20have%20led%20to%20strikes%20by%20thousands%20of%20workers%20from%20all%20major%20platforms.%20While%20the%20bill%20is%20a%20welcome%20first%20step%2C%20it%20should%20be%20noted%20that%20it%20leaves%20much%20to%20be%20desired.%20Most%20notably%2C%20the%20act%20does%20not%20address%20the%20informal%20nature%20of%20gig%20work%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20the%20root%20of%20most%20gig%20workers%E2%80%99%20grievances.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20act%20does%20not%20define%20what%20it%20means%20by%20social%20security%2C%20thus%20leaving%20details%20of%20actual%20benefits%20and%20implementation%20shrouded%20in%20ambiguity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20Rajasthan%20has%20enacted%20an%20impressive%20set%20of%20progressive%20policies%20for%20which%20it%20deserves%20credit.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20note%20that%20the%20actual%20success%20lies%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20these%20schemes%2C%20which%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20While%20the%20intent%20is%20laudable%2C%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20amount%20to%20much%20if%20the%20implementation%20is%20lacklustre.%20The%20Gehlot%20administration%2C%20elsewhere%2C%20has%20also%20been%20accused%20of%20using%20welfare%20only%20as%20a%20means%20to%20remain%20in%20power%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%20Regardless%20of%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20political%20intentions%2C%20it%20should%20be%20noted%20that%20responding%20to%20public%20demand%20and%20needs%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20fundamental%20tenet%20of%20any%20democratic%20society.%20Thus%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20pressurising%20governments%20to%20respond%20to%20people%E2%80%99s%20needs%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20successful%20example%20of%20democracy%20in%20action.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20also%20attracted%20criticism%20for%20doling%20out%20so-called%20freebies%20or%20revdi%2C%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20calls%20it.%20However%2C%20in%20a%20country%20where%20over%2070%20crore%20people%20depend%20on%20PDS%20rations%20to%20survive%2C%20calling%20welfare%20schemes%20%E2%80%98freebies%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98revdi%E2%80%99%20displays%20a%20surprising%20lack%20of%20touch%20with%20the%20socio-economic%20reality%20of%20the%20masses.%20Critics%20of%20welfare%20schemes%20often%20point%20out%20the%20assumed%20unsustainable%20nature%20of%20social%20security%20expenditure.%20While%20it%20is%20true%20that%20certain%20fiscal%20constraints%20bind%20governments%2C%20critics%20often%20weaponise%20these%20constraints%20only%20to%20advocate%20for%20cuts%20in%20social%20spending.%20In%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Feconomy%2Fis-gehlot-destroying-rajasthans-economy-through-freebies-data-shows-this-isnt-the-case%2F1617992%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERajasthan%E2%80%99s%20case%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20however%2C%20the%20fiscal%20deficit%20has%20fallen%20faster%20than%20the%20average%20of%20other%20states%20since%202020-21.%20It%20fell%20by%202.2%25%20of%20GSDP%20between%202020-21%20and%202023-24%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20whereas%20it%20fell%20by%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20GSDP%20for%20other%20states%20on%20average.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20tax%20revenue%20is%20estimated%20to%20increase%20from%206.6%25%20of%20GSDP%20in%202022-23%20to%207.2%25%20of%20GSDP%20this%20year.%20The%20state%20seems%20to%20be%20doing%20well%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20expected%20tax%20revenue%20and%20fiscal%20deficit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20economists%20believe%20that%20a%20demand-side%20push%20through%20welfare%20policies%20that%20increase%20the%20disposable%20income%20of%20low-income%20households%20is%20a%20proven%20method%20of%20reviving%20demand%20in%20the%20economy.%20Simply%20put%2C%20welfare%20expenditure%20allows%20families%20to%20save%20more%20money%20which%20could%20then%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20be%20used%20to%20demand%20other%20goods%20and%20services%2C%20thus%20increasing%20aggregate%20demand%20in%20the%20economy.%C2%A0%20Therefore%2C%20critics%E2%80%99%20concerns%20appear%20to%20be%20founded%20less%20in%20facts%20and%20more%20in%20prejudice%20towards%20welfare.%20Opposing%20%E2%80%98freebies%E2%80%99%20while%20giving%20out%20corporate%20subsidies%20worth%20lakhs%20of%20crores%20is%20not%20only%20bad%20policymaking%20but%20also%20obstructs%20people%20from%20exercising%20their%20right%20to%20live%20with%20human%20dignity%2C%20as%20enshrined%20in%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMohit%20Verma%2C%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20Research%20Associate%20at%20Good%20Business%20Lab%2C%20Bengaluru.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EJapneet%20Singh%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3EResearch%20Associate%20at%20Development%20Solutions%2C%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700559047000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21144259%2F24083848365_f5f794c540_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%