rofit%20organisation%20only%20in%20June%202019.%20A%20month%20before%20they%20officially%20registered%20themselves%20as%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%2C%20they%20opened%20their%20Shelter%20Space%20for%20LGBTQI%2B%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20thing%20we%20know%20as%20queer%20people%20is%20that%20our%20homes%20are%20not%20always%20the%20safest%20spaces.%20Many%20queer%20people%20get%20kicked%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20out%20of%20ignorance%20and%20fear%20of%20what%20the%20larger%20society%20may%20think%20if%20their%20child%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20follow%20conventional%20rules%20of%20gender.%20Many%20queer%20people%20endure%20homelessness.%20In%20addition%20to%20all%20this%2C%20when%20there%20is%20a%20crisis%20like%20COVID-19%20or%20the%20current%20armed%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20place%20to%20stay%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sadam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shelter%20space%20is%20a%20crowdfunded%20initiative%2C%20informs%20Sadam%2C%20where%20queer%20people%2C%20who%20are%20rendered%20homeless%2C%20can%20stay%20for%2010%20days%20free%20of%20charge.%20After%2010%20days%2C%20if%20people%20can%20afford%20it%2C%20they%20are%20asked%20to%20pay%20Rs%20100%20per%20day%20for%20food%2C%20shelter%2C%20clothing%20and%20counselling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20thing%20that%20happens%20when%20anyone%20enters%20this%20shelter%20is%20that%20they%20go%20through%20counselling%20by%20queer-affirmative%20mental%20health%20professionals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20The%20shelter%20does%20not%20currently%20provide%20de-addiction%20and%20psychosocial%20support.%20Queer%20persons%20at%20the%20shelter%20who%20are%20suffering%20from%20addiction%20are%20directed%20to%20reliable%20professionals%20who%20can%20provide%20that%20sort%20of%20care.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20Ya_All%20does%20not%20accept%20calls%20from%20parents%20who%20want%20to%20forcibly%20put%20their%20children%20in%20their%20centres.%20It%E2%80%99s%20imperative%20that%20the%20young%20and%20queer%20person%20in%20question%20gives%20their%20consent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0043-1700226070.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shelter%20for%20Queer%20People%20in%20Manipur%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0043-1700226070.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0043-1700226070-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0043-1700226070-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0043-1700226070-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0043-1700226070-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334371%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShelter%20Space%20for%20queer%20youth%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20task%20is%20to%20provide%20mental%20healthcare%20to%20any%20queer%20persons.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20about%20picking%20up%20people%20from%20the%20streets%20and%20filling%20out%20our%20centre%20just%20to%20get%20funding.%20Our%20work%20is%20to%20provide%20care%20and%20support%20to%20queer%20people%20who%20need%20it.%20As%20queer%20people%20with%20difficult%20lived%20experiences%2C%20we%20understand%20how%20it%20feels.%20For%20us%2C%20empathy%20is%20more%20important%20than%20funding%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Ya_All%20also%20opened%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20de-addiction%20centre%20for%20transgender%20men%2C%20which%20is%20run%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Government%20of%20Manipur.%20Called%20the%20Rainbow%20Trust%20Centre%2C%20it%20offers%20de-addiction%20and%20psychosocial%20support%20for%20two%20months%20free%20of%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20boy%20or%20girl%20identifies%20themselves%20as%20a%20transgender%20man%20or%20woman%2C%20they%20are%20forced%20to%20stay%20in%20rehabilitation%20centres%20catered%20to%20cisgender%20men%20or%20women.%20These%20aren%E2%80%99t%20safe%20spaces.%20Many%20queer%20people%20suffer%20sexual%20assault%20and%20harassment%20at%20these%20centres.%20Parents%20forcefully%20admit%20them%20into%20these%20centres%20for%20recovery%20without%20their%20consent.%20That%20is%20why%20we%20are%20working%20with%20the%20Manipur%20government%E2%80%99s%20social%20welfare%20department%20to%20create%20this%20space%20(de-addiction%20centre)%20for%20transgender%20men.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20new%20initiative%20but%20deeply%20personal%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20768px)%20100vw%2C%20768px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0048-1-1700226140.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Safe%20spaces%20for%20Queer%20People%20in%20Manipur%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0048-1-1700226140.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0048-1-1700226140-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0048-1-1700226140-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0048-1-1700226140-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0048-1-1700226140-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334373%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECreating%20safer%20spaces%20for%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20LGBTQ%2B%20community.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKhudol%20initiatives%20and%20the%20power%20of%20giving%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EKhudol%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20means%20gifts%20in%20Manipuri%2C%20is%20a%20people-led%20initiative%20implemented%20by%20Ya_All%20with%20the%20theme%20%E2%80%98joy%20of%20sharing%E2%80%99.%20The%20objective%20of%20these%20initiatives%20is%20to%20organise%20crowdfunding%20campaigns%20to%20help%20and%20support%20each%20other%20in%20times%20of%20need%20or%20during%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20Khudol%20initiative%20came%20together%20at%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20You%20can%20read%20more%20about%20their%20work%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fthebetterindia%2Fphotos%2Fa.10151330860254594%2F10158757440554594%2F%3Ftype%3D3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202020%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Secretary-General%E2%80%99s%20Envoy%20on%20Youth%20listed%20Khudol%20as%20one%20of%20the%20top%2010%20global%20initiatives%20for%20an%20inclusive%20fight%20against%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20Even%20during%20the%20current%20armed%20conflict%20in%20the%20state%20or%20the%20natural%20disaster%20in%20Sikkim%2C%20Ya_All%20has%20organised%20similar%20Khudol%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20year%20has%20been%20very%20difficult.%20We%20were%20under%20curfew%20for%20six%20months%20with%20our%20internet%20regularly%20disabled.%20There%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20lost%20their%20livelihoods%2C%20homes%20and%20businesses.%20Our%20job%20isn%E2%80%99t%20to%20point%20fingers.%20Our%20task%20as%20young%20queer%20people%2C%20who%20have