re%20(IUCN).%20Among%20these%2C%20%3Cem%3Epaphiopedilum%20druryi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(critically%20endangered)%20and%20%3Cem%3Evanda%20spathulata%20%3C%2Fem%3E(vulnerable)%20are%20the%20two%20threatened%20species%20found%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWayanad%20resident%20Sabu%20has%20devoted%20himself%20to%20conserving%20wild%20orchids.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20innovative%20farmer%20has%20conserved%2060%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F249279%2Forchid-sanctuary-mushroom-arunachal-pradesh-ankit-kumar-ifs-civil-service-wildlife-protection-act-medicinal-plants-tribals-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarieties%20of%20wild%20orchids%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3Evanda%20testacea%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ecymbidium%20aloifolium%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3Cem%3E%20luisia%20zeylanica%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eeria%20mysorensis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Efoxtail%20%3C%2Fem%3Eorchid%20from%20the%20Western%20Ghats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20conserve%20orchids%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20after%20completing%20higher%20studies%20in%20healthcare%20management%2C%20Sabu%20started%20working%20with%20the%20Dr%20Moopens%20Medical%20College%20in%20Wayanad.%20Irrespective%20of%20the%20profession%2C%20he%20was%20motivated%20to%20follow%20his%20passion%20for%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20this%20passion%20that%20took%20him%20to%20nurseries%20several%20times.%20When%20he%20came%20across%20a%20few%20orchids%20at%20the%20nursery%2C%20he%20was%20in%20awe%20of%20the%20breathtaking%20beauty%20of%20the%20flowers.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20very%20tiny%20but%20attractive%20flowers%20available%20in%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20colours%20and%20forms%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2038-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20home%2C%20he%20started%20researching%20about%20orchids%20and%20immersed%20himself%20i