ning%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vihaan's%20winning%20shot%20in%20the%20'10%20years%20and%20under'%20category%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20Photographer%20of%20the%20Year.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334317%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVihaan%E2%80%99s%20winning%20shot%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9910%20years%20and%20under%E2%80%99%20category%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20Photographer%20of%20the%20Year%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vihaan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20caught%20the%20judges%E2%80%99%20eye%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317185%2Fbollywood-celebrity-photographer-munna-thaakur-recalls-struggle-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20composition%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20image.%20As%20Dhritiman%20Mukherjee%2C%20Wildlife%20and%20Conservation%20Photographer%20and%20Competition%20Judge%2C%20comment