0forced%20to%20eat%20poor-quality%20fast%20food.%20They%20remain%20unaware%20of%20the%20amounts%20of%20calories%20that%20go%20into%20their%20diet.%20Most%20of%20the%20restaurants%20use%20food%20colours%2C%20artificial%20flavour%20enhancers%20like%20MSG%2C%20adulterated%20lemon%20salt%2C%20and%20vanaspati.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20launched%20Jagli%20Tindi%20in%202019%2C%20they%20kept%20health%20and%20nutrition%20intrinsic%20to%20the%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20dream%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20time%20we%20were%20dating%2C%20Raksha%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20run%20a%20business%20together.%20Instead%20of%20going%20on%20honeymoon%2C%20we%20started%20the%20restaurant%20just%20six%20months%20after%20our%20marriage.%20This%20is%20our%20first%20baby%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJagli%20Tindi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98food%20relished%20while%20sitting%20on%20a%20traditional%20deck%20area%E2%80%99%20in%20Kannada%2C%20offers%20about%2030%20varieties%20of%20tempting%20Kundapura%20food.%20Priced%20between%20Rs%2015%20and%20Rs%20120%2C%20the%20restaurant%20aims%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F319669%2Fbengaluru-family-starts-traditional-south-indian-food-stall-business-in-brooklyn-swetha-raju%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eserve%20nutritious%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20people%20irrespective%20of%20income%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhas%20says%20his%20restaurant%20attracts%20significant%20footfall%20every%20day.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20people%20from%20across%20Karnataka%20move%20from%20their%20native%20places%20to%20Bangalore%20for%20work.%20Like%20me%2C%20they%20regularly%20crave%20traditional%20food.%20Whenever%20I%20interact%20with%20my%20customers%2C%20they%20tell%20me%20how%20they%20come%20to%20us%20to%20reminisce%20about%20their%20hometowns%20and%20recreate%20memories%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297294%2Fhistory-origin-of-south-india-iconic-drinks-filter-coffee-jigarthanda-tamil-nadu-kerala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhat%20their%20mothers%20cooked%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCw5HcNYL94L%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCw5HcNYL94L%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCw5HcNYL94L%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20J%20A%20G%20L%20I%20T%20I%20N%20D%20I%20(%40jagli_tindi)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20%3Cem%3Emandakki%20upkari%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20among%20the%20bestsellers.%20Served%20on%20a%20banana%20leaf%2C%20the%20delicacy%20is%20made%20with%20red%20puffed%20rice%20and%20is%20tossed%20with%20their%20%E2%80%98secret%E2%80%99%20%3C